WEBVTT

00:42.880 --> 00:44.960
立即到你的岗位报到
Report to your stations immediately.

00:44.960 --> 00:48.470
这不是演习  我们遭到袭击
This is not a drill. We are under attack!

00:49.400 --> 00:51.480
我们遭到袭击
We are under attack!

01:52.210 --> 01:53.130
妈的
Shit!

01:53.140 --> 01:54.310
别说脏话
Language!

01:54.670 --> 01:56.600
贾维斯  从上面看情况如何
Jarvis, what's the view from upstairs?

01:56.750 --> 02:00.490
某种能量护盾保护着里面的建筑物
The central building is protected by some kind of energy shield.

02:00.860 --> 02:01.940
斯托克的科技
Strucker's technology is

02:01.940 --> 02:04.560
远比之前拿下的九头蛇基地先进
well beyond any other Hydra base we've taken.

02:07.530 --> 02:09.370
洛基的权杖一定在里面
Loki's scepter must be here.

02:09.550 --> 02:11.910
没有它  斯托克不可能有这种防御
Strucker couldn't mount this defense without it.

02:12.650 --> 02:14.030
终于
At long last.

02:25.710 --> 02:28.260
"终于"是拖得太久了  小伙子们
"At long last" is lasting a little long, boys.

02:32.430 --> 02:35.720
对  我觉得已经没法出奇制胜了
Yeah. I think we lost the element of surprise.

02:36.870 --> 02:37.500
等一下
Wait a second.

02:37.500 --> 02:38.250
没人想回应一下
No one else is gonna deal

02:38.250 --> 02:41.120
刚才队长说的"别说脏话"吗
with the fact that Cap just said "language"?

02:41.270 --> 02:42.390
我知道
I know.

02:48.850 --> 02:50.210
顺嘴就说出来了
Just slipped out.

02:50.350 --> 02:54.440
<b>九头蛇研究基地</b>

02:51.600 --> 02:54.440
<b>东欧  索科威亚</b>

02:55.940 --> 02:57.440
谁下的攻击命令
Who gave the order to attack?

02:57.450 --> 02:59.570
斯托克先生  复仇者来了
Herr Strucker, it's the Avengers.

02:59.970 --> 03:02.780
他们在森林外围着陆  外围守卫慌了
They landed in the far woods. The perimeter guard panicked.

03:03.330 --> 03:05.280
他们一定是为权杖而来
They have to be after the scepter.

03:06.090 --> 03:08.450
-我们能挡住他们吗  -他们可是复仇者
- Can we hold them? - They're the Avengers.

03:08.450 --> 03:10.290
部署所有坦克
Deploy the rest of the tanks.

03:10.290 --> 03:12.350
集中火力猛攻弱点
Concentrate fire on the weak ones.

03:12.630 --> 03:15.450
攻击可能会让他们团结起来
A hit may make them close ranks.

03:16.440 --> 03:18.510
我们取得的一切成就...
Everything we've accomplished...

03:18.570 --> 03:20.600
但我们马上就要取得最大的突破了
But we're on the verge of our greatest breakthrough.

03:20.600 --> 03:23.170
那就让他们瞧瞧我们的成就
Then let's show them what we've accomplished.

03:23.480 --> 03:25.110
派出双胞胎
Send out the twins.

03:25.620 --> 03:26.870
太早了
It's too soon.

03:27.590 --> 03:29.300
他们当初加入就是为了这个
It's what they signed up for.

03:30.010 --> 03:31.910
我的手下能挡住他们
My men can hold them.

03:39.500 --> 03:42.140
先生  城市受了打击
Sir, the city is taking fire.

03:44.640 --> 03:47.820
我们知道斯托克不在乎平民伤亡
Well, we know Strucker's not gonna worry about civilian casualties.

03:48.690 --> 03:50.430
派出钢铁军团
Send in the Iron Legion.

03:54.940 --> 03:57.990
这一地区很危险  请撤离
This quadrant is unsafe. Please back away.

03:58.460 --> 03:59.950
我们是来帮你们的
We are here to help.

04:01.140 --> 04:04.070
这一地区很危险  请撤离
This quadrant is unsafe. Please back away.

04:04.860 --> 04:06.220
请撤离
Please back away.

04:06.630 --> 04:08.270
-我们想减少附带损失  -科斯特尔
- We wish to avoid collateral damage. - Costel!

04:08.270 --> 04:11.260
这场冲突一结束  我们就通知你们
We will inform you when this current conflict is resolved.

04:11.260 --> 04:14.160
-我们是来帮你们的  -复仇者  回家去吧
- We are here to help. - Avengers, go home!

04:15.720 --> 04:17.200
我们是来帮你们的
We are here to help.

04:18.010 --> 04:19.770
我们决不屈服
We will not yield!

04:20.440 --> 04:24.260
美国人派他们的怪物来考验我们
The Americans sent their circus freaks to test us.

04:24.260 --> 04:26.900
我们把他们的尸体送回去
We will send them back in bags.

04:29.060 --> 04:32.100
-决不投降  -决不投降
- No surrender! - No surrender!

04:33.190 --> 04:35.310
我准备投降
I am going to surrender.

04:35.780 --> 04:37.480
你得把一切都删除
You delete everything.

04:37.530 --> 04:39.190
如果把武器留给复仇者
If we give the Avengers the weapons,

04:39.190 --> 04:40.530
他们可能不会深入调查我们的研究...
they may not look too far into what we've been...

04:40.530 --> 04:41.790
双胞胎呢
The twins.

04:41.800 --> 04:44.080
-他们还没准备好...  -不  我是问
- They are not ready to take on... - No, no, I mean...

04:45.600 --> 04:46.860
双胞胎呢
Twins.

05:13.240 --> 05:14.740
没预见到吗
You didn't see that coming?

05:21.560 --> 05:22.640
克林特
Clint!

05:26.230 --> 05:27.420
战场上有个能力增强者
We have an Enhanced in the field.

05:27.420 --> 05:28.570
克林特中弹了
Clint's hit!

05:32.690 --> 05:34.390
来个人解决掉地堡
Somebody want to deal with that bunker?

05:38.480 --> 05:39.560
谢谢
Thank you.

05:46.510 --> 05:49.270
斯塔克  我们得进去
Stark, we really need to get inside.

05:49.630 --> 05:50.820
我正在接近
I'm closing in.

05:54.040 --> 05:56.080
贾维斯  我接近了吧
Jarvis, am I closing in?

05:56.860 --> 05:58.560
你看见保护盾的能量源了吗
Do you see a power source for that shield?

05:58.560 --> 06:01.180
北面塔楼下面有道粒子波
There's a particle wave below the north tower.

06:01.180 --> 06:02.930
好  来戳破这层护盾
Great, I want to poke it with something.

06:11.260 --> 06:12.990
城门吊桥放下来了  各位
The drawbridge is down, people.

06:17.180 --> 06:18.420
能力增强者
The Enhanced?

06:18.650 --> 06:19.760
他一闪而过
He's a blur.

06:20.060 --> 06:22.240
没见过这样的新人
All the new players we've faced, I've never seen this.

06:22.550 --> 06:23.810
其实我就没看到他
In fact, I still haven't.

06:23.820 --> 06:26.490
克林特的伤势很严重  各位  我们得撤退
Clint's hit pretty bad, guys. We're gonna need evac.

06:26.490 --> 06:29.430
我可以把巴顿带到飞机那  越快越好
I can get Barton to the jet. The sooner we're gone, the better.

06:29.430 --> 06:31.970
-你和斯塔克去取权杖  -收到
- You and Stark secure the scepter. - Copy that.

06:33.590 --> 06:34.910
他们好像站成一队了
Looks like they're lining up.

06:35.250 --> 06:36.670
见到偶像激动了
Well, they're excited.

06:40.650 --> 06:41.860
找到权杖
Find the scepter.

06:42.800 --> 06:45.640
我的天哪  别说脏话
And for gosh sake, watch your language!

06:46.820 --> 06:48.820
你是抓住这个不打算放了
That's not going away any time soon.

06:54.370 --> 06:56.760
各位先住手  有话好好说
Guys, stop. We gotta talk this through.

07:00.010 --> 07:02.300
-说得真好  -才不是
- It was a good talk. - No, it wasn't.

07:08.640 --> 07:09.880
警戒模式
Sentry mode.

07:12.530 --> 07:15.080
好了  贾维斯  我全都要
Okay, Jarvis, you know. I want it all.

07:15.210 --> 07:17.140
记得抄送总部的希尔
Make sure you copy Hill at HQ.

07:20.960 --> 07:22.380
外面已经安全了
We're locked down out here.

07:22.760 --> 07:25.330
那就去找班纳  该唱摇篮曲了
Then get to Banner. Time for a lullaby.

07:28.700 --> 07:30.550
我知道你藏的不止是文件
I know you're hiding more than files.

07:31.890 --> 07:34.700
小贾  给我房间的红外扫描图  快点
Hey, J, give me an IR scan of the room, real quick.

07:34.730 --> 07:36.130
你左边的墙
The wall to your left.

07:36.380 --> 07:38.580
我探测到钢筋
I'm reading steel reinforcement

07:39.220 --> 07:40.630
还有气流
and an air current.

07:41.720 --> 07:42.500
千万要是道暗门
Please be a secret door.

07:42.500 --> 07:44.830
千万要是道暗门  千万要是道暗门
Please be a secret door. Please be a secret door.

07:45.620 --> 07:46.720
耶
Yay.

08:02.160 --> 08:03.310
大块头
Hey, big guy.

08:07.140 --> 08:08.780
太阳快下山了
Sun's getting real low.

09:12.260 --> 09:13.580
斯托克男爵
Baron Strucker.

09:14.130 --> 09:15.910
九头蛇的头号恶棍
Hydra's number one thug.

09:16.930 --> 09:19.540
严格来说  是神盾局的恶棍
Technically, I'm a thug for S.H.I.E.L.D.

09:19.540 --> 09:21.680
严格来说  你被炒鱿鱼了
Well, then technically you're unemployed.

09:22.070 --> 09:23.540
洛基的权杖在哪
Where's Loki's scepter?

09:24.050 --> 09:26.380
别着急  真栽了我心里有数
Don't worry, I know when I'm beat.

09:26.680 --> 09:29.330
希望你能提一句说我很合作
You'll mention how I cooperated, I hope.

09:29.330 --> 09:32.230
我就加在非法人体实验后面
I'll put it right under "illegal human experimentation."

09:33.160 --> 09:34.450
有几个
How many are there?

09:39.530 --> 09:43.030
第二名能力增强者  女性  不要交手
We have a second Enhanced. Female. Do not engage.

09:44.140 --> 09:45.830
你可得再快点才
You'll have to be faster than...

09:50.620 --> 09:51.990
各位  我找到斯托克了
Guys, I got Strucker.

09:52.330 --> 09:56.340
是吗  我找到了个更大的
Yeah, I got something bigger.

10:19.430 --> 10:20.430
托尔
Thor,

10:21.480 --> 10:22.940
我发现目标了
I got eyes on the prize.

11:12.930 --> 11:16.830
你本来能救我们的
You could have saved us.

11:24.290 --> 11:26.570
你为什么没再努力一点
Why didn't you do more?

12:04.050 --> 12:05.870
我们就这么让他拿走吗
We're just gonna let him take it?

12:15.170 --> 12:19.380
复

12:15.170 --> 12:19.380
仇

12:15.170 --> 12:19.380
者

12:15.170 --> 12:19.380
联

12:15.170 --> 12:19.380
盟

12:15.170 --> 12:19.380
2

12:17.250 --> 12:22.880
<b>奥  创  纪  元</b>

12:28.860 --> 12:34.420
歌剧《诺尔玛》选段  《圣洁的女神》咏叹调

12:57.590 --> 12:59.710
这次摇篮曲效率很高呢
Hey, the lullaby worked better than ever.

13:01.390 --> 13:03.440
只是没想到需要我变绿
Just wasn't expecting a code green.

13:03.440 --> 13:04.140
如果不是你
You hadn't been there,

13:04.140 --> 13:06.410
我们的伤亡恐怕得加倍了
there would have been double the casualties.

13:07.560 --> 13:10.680
我最好的朋友可能也会成为回忆
My best friend would've been a treasured memory.

13:10.910 --> 13:12.810
其实有时候我连自己想听到的话
You know, sometimes exactly what I want to hear

13:12.810 --> 13:14.930
都不想听到
isn't exactly what I want to hear.

13:15.900 --> 13:17.700
你什么时候才能信任我
How long before you trust me?

13:19.680 --> 13:21.420
我不是不信任你
It's not you I don't trust.

13:23.290 --> 13:24.890
托尔  绿巨人怎么样
Thor, report on the Hulk.

13:25.120 --> 13:28.370
冥府充斥着他送去的敌人的惨叫
The gates of Hel are filled with the screams of his victims.

13:30.240 --> 13:31.660
但不是因为死掉惨叫  绝对不是
But not the screams of the dead, of course.

13:31.660 --> 13:33.200
是受伤的惨叫
No, no, wounded screams.

13:33.200 --> 13:35.500
只是呻吟  还有不少抱怨
Mainly whimpering, a great deal of complaining

13:35.500 --> 13:40.040
抱怨扭伤  撞伤什么的
and tales of sprained deltoids and gout.

13:40.040 --> 13:42.890
班纳  赵医生正从首尔赶过来
Hey, Banner, Dr. Cho is on her way in from Seoul.

13:42.890 --> 13:44.980
可以让她在你实验室布置手术台吗
Is it okay if she sets up in your lab?

13:44.980 --> 13:47.060
-可以  她知道该怎么做  -谢谢
- Yeah, she knows her way around. - Thanks.

13:47.060 --> 13:48.030
让她把东西准备齐全
Tell her to prep everything.

13:48.030 --> 13:49.340
巴顿这次需要全面治疗
Barton's gonna need the full treatment.

13:49.350 --> 13:51.570
-好的  先生  -贾维斯  你来开
- Very good, sir. - Jarvis, take the wheel.

13:51.580 --> 13:52.720
是  先生
Yes, sir.

13:53.340 --> 13:55.040
航向锁定
Approach vector is locked.

13:54.270 --> 13:56.180
贾维斯是我的飞行搭档

13:55.820 --> 13:57.270
感觉不错吧
Feels good, yeah?

13:57.610 --> 13:58.490
自从神盾局瓦解
I mean, you've been after this thing

13:58.490 --> 13:59.920
你就一直在追踪它的下落
since S.H.I.E.L.D. collapsed.

13:59.920 --> 14:01.840
我跟大伙扫荡基地是挺开心  只是...
Not that I haven't enjoyed our little raiding parties, but...

14:01.840 --> 14:04.600
没错  但找到了这个  就要到头了
No, but this... this brings it to a close.

14:05.060 --> 14:07.420
剩下的就是弄清楚它都用来干了什么
As soon as we find out what else this has been used for.

14:07.420 --> 14:08.780
不光是武器
I don't just mean weapons.

14:08.780 --> 14:10.970
斯托克什么时候也能弄出能力增强者了
Since when is Strucker capable of human enhancement?

14:10.970 --> 14:11.810
班纳和我想
Banner and I will give it

14:11.810 --> 14:13.420
在还回阿斯加德前检查一下
the once over before it goes back to Asgard.

14:13.420 --> 14:14.610
可以吗
Is that cool with you?

14:14.920 --> 14:17.550
就几天  告别会前就还你
Just a few days till the farewell party.

14:17.660 --> 14:18.650
告别会你来的  对吧
You're staying, right?

14:19.140 --> 14:22.510
是  当然  胜利应该以狂欢来庆祝
Yes, yes, of course. A victory should be honored with revels.

14:22.560 --> 14:25.000
就是  谁不爱狂欢呢  队长
Yeah, who doesn't love revels? Captain?

14:25.000 --> 14:27.370
希望奇塔瑞和九头蛇的事这下都了结了
Hopefully this puts an end to the Chitauri and Hydra.

14:27.370 --> 14:30.370
所以好吧  狂欢
So, yes, revels.

15:03.720 --> 15:05.130
实验室布置完毕  老大
Lab's all set up, boss.

15:05.130 --> 15:06.380
其实  他才是老大
Actually, he's the boss.

15:06.380 --> 15:09.200
我只是负责结账  设计一切
I just pay for everything and design everything

15:09.300 --> 15:10.610
还有让大家看起来酷一点
and make everyone look cooler.

15:10.610 --> 15:11.910
斯托克有消息了吗
What's the word on Strucker?

15:11.910 --> 15:12.620
在北约那呢
NATO's got him.

15:12.620 --> 15:13.800
两个能力增强者呢
The two Enhanced?

15:13.860 --> 15:16.700
旺达和皮特·马克西莫夫  双胞胎
Wanda and Pietro Maximoff. Twins.

15:16.700 --> 15:19.770
十岁时轰炸机毁了他们家  成了孤儿
Orphaned at 10 when a shell collapsed their apartment building.

15:19.930 --> 15:22.390
索科威亚有过段艰辛的历史
Sokovia's had a rough history.

15:22.400 --> 15:25.990
是个平凡的地方  但是能通往好多要地
It's nowhere special, but it's on the way to everywhere special.

15:25.990 --> 15:26.860
他们什么能力
Their abilities?

15:26.860 --> 15:30.270
他新陈代谢很快  体温控制能力超强
He's got increased metabolism and improved thermal homeostasis.

15:30.270 --> 15:32.170
她的特长是干扰神经电传导
Her thing is neuroelectric interfacing,

15:32.170 --> 15:34.630
拥有念力  能控制心智
telekinesis, mental manipulation.

15:35.540 --> 15:37.200
他很快  她很怪
He's fast and she's weird.

15:37.890 --> 15:39.460
他们还会再露面的
Well, they're gonna show up again.

15:39.590 --> 15:43.420
同意  文件说他们自愿加入实验的
Agreed. File says they volunteered for Strucker's experiments.

15:43.700 --> 15:45.650
-疯了  -确实
- It's nuts. - Right.

15:45.820 --> 15:47.670
什么样的怪物才会为了保护自己的国家
What kind of monster would let a German scientist

15:47.670 --> 15:50.260
让一个德国科学家在自己身上做实验啊
experiment on them to protect their country?

15:50.650 --> 15:52.560
我们不在战争时期  队长
We're not at war, Captain.

15:52.850 --> 15:53.980
但他们在
They are.

16:24.480 --> 16:25.410
他怎么样了
How's he doing?

16:25.410 --> 16:27.240
很不幸  他还是巴顿
Unfortunately, he's still Barton.

16:27.240 --> 16:28.300
太糟了
That's terrible.

16:28.300 --> 16:29.790
他没事  就是渴了
He's fine. He's thirsty.

16:30.010 --> 16:32.450
好了  醒醒贾维斯  游戏时间到
All right. Look alive, Jarvis. It's playtime.

16:33.380 --> 16:35.050
这玩具只能玩几天
We've only got a couple of days with this joystick,

16:35.050 --> 16:36.770
一定得好好利用
so let's make the most of it.

16:37.240 --> 16:40.290
显示最新结构组成分析
Update me on the structural and compositional analysis.

16:41.930 --> 16:43.360
权杖来自外星
The scepter is alien.

16:44.100 --> 16:46.150
有些元素我无法确定
There are elements I can't quantify.

16:46.150 --> 16:47.720
就是说还有能确定的元素
So there's elements you can?

16:47.720 --> 16:49.830
宝石似乎是个保护罩
The jewel appears to be a protective housing

16:49.840 --> 16:51.590
保护里面的东西
for something inside,

16:51.720 --> 16:53.160
它力量强大
something powerful.

16:53.160 --> 16:54.030
类似反应堆吗
Like a reactor?

16:54.030 --> 16:55.440
类似电脑
Like a computer.

16:55.600 --> 16:58.000
我破译的应该是代码
I believe I'm deciphering code.

17:00.370 --> 17:01.880
你确定他不会有事吗
Are you sure he's gonna be okay?

17:02.960 --> 17:05.240
大家就是靠假装需要他才团结起来的
Pretending to need this guy really brings the team together.

17:05.240 --> 17:08.000
没有恶化的可能
There's no possibility of deterioration.

17:08.000 --> 17:11.060
分子桥的作用是瞬时的
The nano-molecular functionality is instantaneous.

17:11.060 --> 17:13.150
他的细胞不会发现是在和拟生体结合
His cells don't know they're bonding with simulacra.

17:13.150 --> 17:15.240
她是在人造生物组织
She's creating tissue.

17:15.360 --> 17:16.990
如果直接去我的实验室
