- It's physics. - Physics.

28:01.320 --> 28:03.990
如果我举起来  就统治阿斯加德了吗
Right, so, if I lift it, I then rule Asgard?

28:03.990 --> 28:05.170
没错
Yes, of course.

28:05.740 --> 28:08.600
我要恢复领主初夜权
I will be reinstituting prima nocta.

28:12.810 --> 28:13.950
马上回来
I'll be right back.

28:21.770 --> 28:22.790
你真用力了吗
Are you even pulling?

28:22.790 --> 28:23.880
你跟我一伙的吗
Are you on my team?

28:23.950 --> 28:25.140
我代表你  用力
Just represent. Pull.

28:25.140 --> 28:26.130
好了  来
All right, let's go.

28:36.580 --> 28:38.030
上吧  史蒂夫  别有压力
Go ahead, Steve. No pressure.

28:41.220 --> 28:42.250
加油  队长
Come on, Cap.

28:51.070 --> 28:52.010
没反应
Nothing.

28:54.660 --> 28:55.890
黑寡妇呢
And, Widow?

28:55.960 --> 28:57.900
不用了  我不好奇自己能不能举起来
No, no. That's not a question I need answered.

28:57.900 --> 29:00.420
虽然我很尊敬你  但这锤子动了手脚
All deference to the Man Who Wouldn't Be King, but it's rigged.

29:00.420 --> 29:01.550
可不他妈是吗
You bet your ass.

29:01.550 --> 29:03.490
史蒂夫  他说脏话了
Steve, he said a bad language word.

29:03.490 --> 29:04.340
你还四处宣扬吗
Did you tell everyone about that?

29:04.340 --> 29:06.740
把手有识别功能  像是安保密码
The handle's imprinted, right? Like a security code.

29:06.740 --> 29:08.660
"无论是谁  只要有托尔的指纹"
"Whosoever is carrying Thor's fingerprints"

29:08.660 --> 29:10.170
锤子上的话是这个意思吧
is, I think, the literal translation.

29:10.170 --> 29:13.970
是啊  这个说法很有意思
Yes. It's a very, very interesting theory.

29:13.970 --> 29:15.200
我有个更简单的
I have a simpler one.

29:17.040 --> 29:18.480
你们都配不上
You're all not worthy.

29:19.600 --> 29:20.770
得了吧
Come on!

29:24.840 --> 29:30.280
配得上
Worthy.

29:35.130 --> 29:36.410
不
No.

29:38.600 --> 29:40.430
你们怎么能配得上
How could you be worthy?

29:42.090 --> 29:43.780
你们都是杀手
You're all killers.

29:43.880 --> 29:45.400
-斯塔克  -贾维斯
- Stark. - Jarvis.

29:45.400 --> 29:47.370
抱歉  我睡着了
I'm sorry, I was asleep.

29:47.650 --> 29:50.370
或者做了个梦
Or I was a-dream.

29:50.370 --> 29:51.350
重启军团操作系统  有战衣出故障了
Reboot Legionnaire OS. We got a buggy suit.

29:51.350 --> 29:54.660
有吵人的声音
There was this terrible noise.

29:54.770 --> 29:56.490
我被线缆...
And I was tangled in...

29:57.460 --> 29:58.610
给...
in...

29:59.170 --> 30:00.920
缠住了
strings.

30:01.360 --> 30:04.860
我只能杀了那家伙  他还挺好的
I had to kill the other guy. He was a good guy.

30:04.860 --> 30:05.930
你杀了谁
You killed someone?

30:05.930 --> 30:07.690
我一开始也不想
Wouldn't have been my first call.

30:08.220 --> 30:12.220
但在现实世界里  脏了手是难免的
But, down in the real world, we're faced with ugly choices.

30:12.220 --> 30:13.300
谁派你来的
Who sent you?

30:13.670 --> 30:16.320
我的设想是保护世界的战衣
I see a suit of armor around the world.

30:17.600 --> 30:19.950
-奥创  -正是本人[肉体]
- Ultron. - In the flesh.

30:19.980 --> 30:21.900
不对  还没肉体
Or, no, not yet.

30:22.190 --> 30:25.060
这束缚着我的茧不算
Not this chrysalis.

30:25.230 --> 30:26.380
但我准备好了
But I'm ready.

30:27.670 --> 30:28.930
我在执行任务
I'm on mission.

30:29.780 --> 30:33.200
-什么任务  -我们时代的和平
- What mission? - Peace in our time.

30:46.460 --> 30:47.530
罗德
Rhodey!

30:57.060 --> 30:57.970
抱歉
Sorry.

30:57.970 --> 30:59.610
-别变绿  -不会的
- Don't turn green. - I won't.

31:13.560 --> 31:14.510
走
Come on!

31:31.740 --> 31:33.020
-斯塔克  -我们是来帮你们的
- Stark! - We are here to help.

31:33.030 --> 31:34.090
稍等  稍等  我能搞定
One sec. One sec, I got this.

31:34.090 --> 31:35.530
我们是来帮你们的
We are here to help.

31:38.280 --> 31:39.670
请退后
Please back away.

31:44.630 --> 31:45.570
托尔
Thor!

31:46.660 --> 31:48.100
不安全...不安全...
...is unsafe. ...is unsafe...

31:48.100 --> 31:51.140
-别这样  这还差不多  -不安全
- Come on! That's the one. - ...is unsafe.

31:54.860 --> 31:55.830
队长
Hey, Cap!

32:02.300 --> 32:04.080
闹得这么大
That was dramatic.

32:05.040 --> 32:07.570
抱歉  我知道你是好心
I'm sorry, I know you mean well.

32:07.660 --> 32:09.640
你只是没想周全
You just didn't think it through.

32:10.970 --> 32:14.730
你想保护世界  又不想改变世界
You want to protect the world but you don't want it to change.

32:15.260 --> 32:17.540
不允许人类进化
How is humanity saved

32:17.540 --> 32:21.180
怎么可能拯救人类
if it's not allowed to evolve?

32:22.700 --> 32:26.290
用这些吗  这种傀儡
With these? These puppets.

32:28.570 --> 32:31.240
想和平只有一条路
There's only one path to peace.

32:32.610 --> 32:34.640
消灭复仇者
The Avengers' extinction.

32:40.970 --> 32:44.910
我曾被线束缚  现在我自由了
I had strings, but now I'm free.

32:49.800 --> 32:53.650
我身上没有线了
There are no strings on me

32:53.700 --> 32:57.130
我身上没有线了
There are no strings on me

32:58.540 --> 33:01.430
看到没  我身上没有线了[出自《匹诺曹》]
But you can see there are no strings on me

33:03.260 --> 33:04.700
我们的心血都没了
All our work is gone.

33:05.380 --> 33:08.260
奥创给清光了  他用互联网逃走了
Ultron cleared out. He used the Internet as an escape hatch.

33:08.260 --> 33:09.090
奥创
Ultron.

33:09.090 --> 33:12.200
他什么都看过了  文件  监控
He's been in everything. Files, surveillance.

33:12.570 --> 33:15.040
对我们的了解估计比彼此都深刻
Probably knows more about us than we know about each other.

33:15.040 --> 33:17.400
他看了你的文件  进了互联网
He's in your files, he's in the Internet.

33:17.780 --> 33:20.640
他要是想找更刺激的东西怎么办
What if he decides to access something a little more exciting?

33:20.640 --> 33:21.460
核武器密码
Nuclear codes.

33:21.470 --> 33:22.800
核武器密码
Nuclear codes.

33:22.800 --> 33:26.200
我们得打几个电话  前提是还能打
Look, we need to make some calls, assuming we still can.

33:26.470 --> 33:28.380
核弹  他说要我们的命
Nukes? He said he wanted us dead.

33:28.380 --> 33:31.230
他没说"要命"  说的是"消灭"
He didn't say "dead." He said "extinct."

33:31.230 --> 33:33.080
他还说自己杀了谁
He also said he killed somebody.

33:33.080 --> 33:35.050
这里没别人了啊
There wasn't anyone else in the building.

33:35.570 --> 33:36.670
有的
Yes, there was.

33:44.220 --> 33:45.260
什么
What?

33:49.460 --> 33:50.770
太疯狂了
This is insane.

33:51.110 --> 33:52.770
贾维斯是第一道防线
Jarvis was the first line of defense.

33:52.770 --> 33:54.780
他要是还在  肯定会关闭奥创的
He would have shut Ultron down. It makes sense.

33:54.780 --> 33:57.890
不  奥创本可以把贾维斯同化
No. Ultron could have assimilated Jarvis.

33:57.890 --> 34:00.880
这不是策略  这是
This isn't strategy. This is

34:01.570 --> 34:02.760
愤怒
rage.

34:05.000 --> 34:05.890
怒火扩散开了
It's going around.

34:05.890 --> 34:06.860
别这样  动口不动手  哥们
Come on, use your words, buddy.

34:06.860 --> 34:09.350
跟你动口还不简单  斯塔克
I have more than enough words to describe you, Stark.

34:09.350 --> 34:11.390
托尔  军团
Thor. The Legionnaire.

34:13.800 --> 34:17.230
跟了一百英里就不见了  但是向北去了
Trail went cold about 100 miles out, but it's headed north.

34:17.640 --> 34:19.150
它拿了权杖
And it has the scepter.

34:19.370 --> 34:21.110
又得麻烦大伙拿回来了
Now we have to retrieve it, again.

34:21.110 --> 34:22.820
灯神已经飞出了神灯
Genie's out of that bottle.

34:23.120 --> 34:24.550
奥创是当务之急
Clear and present is Ultron.

34:24.550 --> 34:26.020
我不明白
I don't understand.

34:26.700 --> 34:28.510
你自己编写的程序
You built this program.

34:30.540 --> 34:32.050
为什么要杀我们
Why is it trying to kill us?

34:38.600 --> 34:39.940
你觉得好笑吗
You think this is funny?

34:40.690 --> 34:41.670
不
No.

34:42.580 --> 34:44.630
应该不好笑吧
It's probably not, right?

34:45.590 --> 34:48.030
真是糟糕  真是...
This is very terrible. Is it so...

34:48.030 --> 34:50.180
真是...  真是糟糕
Is it so... It is. It's so terrible.

34:50.180 --> 34:51.210
如果不是你
This could have been avoided

34:51.210 --> 34:52.130
乱摆弄自己不懂的东西  就不会到这步
if you hadn't played with something you don't understand.

34:52.130 --> 34:56.460
不  对不起  对不起  是很好笑
No. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. It is funny.

34:56.460 --> 34:58.650
你不懂我们为什么需要这个真是好笑
It's a hoot that you don't get why we need this.

34:58.650 --> 35:01.020
托尼  现在说这个不好吧
Tony, maybe this might not be the time.

35:01.020 --> 35:02.950
真的吗  就这样
Really? That's it?

35:03.570 --> 35:06.340
一有人发火  你就跑过来当和事佬
You just roll over, show your belly every time somebody snarls?

35:06.340 --> 35:08.110
我造了个杀人机器人时才这样
Only when I've created a murder bot.

35:08.110 --> 35:11.690
没有  差得远呢  连界面都差得远呢吧
We didn't. We weren't even close. Were we close to an interface?

35:11.690 --> 35:14.640
至少你做对了点什么  就在这
Well, you did something right. And you did it right here.

35:15.510 --> 35:17.360
复仇者联盟不应该像神盾局一样
The Avengers were supposed to be different than S.H.I.E.L.D.

35:17.360 --> 35:20.370
还有人记得我扛着核弹穿过虫洞吗
Anybody remember when I carried a nuke through a wormhole?

35:20.370 --> 35:22.060
-没想起来  -拯救了纽约
- No, it's never come up. - Saved New York?

35:22.060 --> 35:23.690
-没听说过  -还记得吗
- Never heard that. - Recall that?

35:24.140 --> 35:28.100
一支外星人大军穿过虫洞入侵地球
A hostile alien army came charging through a hole in space.

35:28.490 --> 35:30.140
我们就在虫洞正下面
We're standing 300 feet below it.

35:32.410 --> 35:33.650
我们是复仇者联盟
We're the Avengers.

35:33.950 --> 35:36.020
我们可以天天抓军火商玩
We can bust arms dealers all the livelong day,

35:36.020 --> 35:38.320
但上面那个虫洞...
but that up there, that's...

35:39.140 --> 35:40.420
那种残局
That's the endgame.

35:41.580 --> 35:43.250
那种敌人你们怎么打败
How were you guys planning on beating that?

35:44.420 --> 35:45.490
齐心协力
Together.

35:49.240 --> 35:50.290
我们会输的
We'll lose.

35:51.650 --> 35:53.390
那就一起输
Then we'll do that together, too.

35:56.510 --> 35:58.970
托尔说得对  奥创在挑战我们
Thor's right. Ultron's calling us out.

35:59.550 --> 36:02.030
我要在他准备好之前找到他
And I'd like to find him before he's ready for us.

36:02.790 --> 36:06.210
世界这么大  先缩小下范围
The world's a big place. Let's start making it smaller.

36:29.710 --> 36:31.860
说吧  如果你浪费了我们的时间...
Talk, and if you are wasting our time...

36:31.870 --> 36:35.570
你们知道这教堂是城市的正中心吗
Did you know this church is in the exact center of the city?

36:36.410 --> 36:37.800
先人们决定建在这
The elders decreed it so

36:37.800 --> 36:41.500
这样大家能离上帝一样近
that everyone could be equally close to God.

36:41.570 --> 36:42.720
我喜欢
I like that.

36:42.940 --> 36:45.140
信仰的几何学
The geometry of belief.

36:47.180 --> 36:50.000
你在好奇为什么看不透我的意识
You're wondering why you can't look inside my head.

36:50.000 --> 36:51.650
有时候是很难
Sometimes it's hard.

36:52.100 --> 36:55.390
但不管什么人  早晚会现形的
But sooner or later, every man shows himself.

36:56.290 --> 36:57.850
可不是嘛
I'm sure they do.

36:58.550 --> 37:01.500
可你不止需要一个"人"
But you needed something more than a man.

37:01.840 --> 37:04.550
所以你才让斯塔克拿走权杖
That's why you let Stark take the scepter.

37:04.760 --> 37:06.470
我没想到
I didn't expect,

37:08.140 --> 37:10.250
但我看到了斯塔克的恐惧
but I saw Stark's fear.

37:10.830 --> 37:12.250
知道他会被恐惧控制
I knew it would control him.

37:12.250 --> 37:14.120
最终毁灭自己
Make him self-destruct.

37:14.120 --> 37:16.870
恐惧的事物都是自己创造的
Everyone creates the thing they dread.

37:17.410 --> 37:20.280
和平人士创造了战争机器
Men of peace create engines of war.

37:20.520 --> 37:22.920
入侵者创造了复仇者
Invaders create Avengers.

37:23.000 --> 37:24.460
人类创造了
People create

37:25.810 --> 37:27.180
更小的人
smaller people?

37:28.620 --> 37:31.340
"孩子"  忘了怎么说了
"Children." I lost the word, there.

37:31.340 --> 37:32.430
孩子
Children

37:32.810 --> 37:35.140
用来取代他们
designed to supplant them,

37:35.140 --> 37:38.560
帮助他们消亡
to help them end.

37:38.570 --> 37:42.190
你来是为这个吗  让复仇者消亡
Is that why you've come, to end the Avengers?

37:42.190 --> 37:44.190
我是来拯救世界的
I've come to save the world.

37:45.140 --> 37:47.990
不过你也没说错
But also... Yeah.

37:51.850 --> 37:53.330
我们马上走
We'll move out right away.

37:53.780 --> 37:54.720
这只是个开始
This is a start,

37:54.720 --> 37:57.080
想要开工  还需要点别的
but there's something we need to begin the real work.

37:57.090 --> 37:59.380
-这些都是...  -我
- All of these are... - Me.

37:59.550 --> 38:02.980
我有样东西复仇者永远不会有  和谐
I have what the Avengers never will. Harmony.

38:03.140 --> 38:05.560
他们就是盘散沙
They're discordant. Disconnected.

38:05.560 --> 38:07.480
斯塔克已经让他们之间有了敌意
Stark's already got them turning on each other.

38:07.480 --> 38:10.050
等你进入了他们的意识
And when you get inside the rest of their heads...

38:10.050 --> 38:12.250
别人都没打算杀他们
Everyone's plan is not to kill them.

38:12.250 --> 38:14.000
让他们成为殉道者吗
And make them martyrs?

38:14.440 --> 38:15.790
得有耐心
You need patience.

38:16.240 --> 38:17.760
得看大局[照片]
Need to see the big picture.

38:17.910 --> 38:21.590
我看不到大局  我只有张小照片
I don't see the big picture. I have a little picture.

38:22.370 --> 38:24.370
我经常拿出来看
I take it out and look at it,

38:25.160 --> 38:26.080
每天都是
every day.

38:26.080 --> 38:29.150
你们的父母在轰炸中丧生  我看了档案
You lost your parents in the bombings. I've seen the records.

38:29.150 --> 38:30.600
档案又不是照片
The records are not the picture.

38:30.600 --> 38:31.330
皮特
Pietro.

38:31.330 --> 38:33.600
不  说吧
No, please.

38:35.920 --> 38:39.130
我们才十岁  一家四口吃着晚饭
We were 10 years old. Having dinner, the four of us.

38:40.660 --> 38:42.440
第一枚炸弹击中了下面两层楼
When the first shell hits, two floors below,

38:42.440 --> 38:44.330
楼板破了个洞
it makes a hole in the floor.

38:44.820 --> 38:45.980
好大的洞
It's big.

38:47.700 --> 38:49.130
爸妈掉了下去
Our parents go in

38:49.720 --> 38:52.970
整栋楼都开始倒塌
and the whole building starts coming apart.

38:53.470 --> 38:54.780
我抓住她
I grab her,

38:55.670 --> 38:58.090
躲到了床下  然后是第二枚
roll under the bed, and the second shell hits.

38:58.090 --> 39:00.090
可是没有爆炸
But it doesn't go off.

39:02.200 --> 39:03.280
它就
It just

39:04.230 --> 39:05.820
在那静静待着
sits there in the rubble.

39:07.160 --> 39:09.070
离我们只有三英尺
Three feet from our faces.

39:10.650 --> 39:14.200
炸弹旁边印着一个词
And on the side of the shell is painted one word.

39:14.200 --> 39:15.430
"斯塔克"
"Stark."

39:17.630 --> 39:19.610
我们被困在那两天
We were trapped for two days.

39:20.290 --> 39:22.670
每次有人想救我们
Every effort to save us,

39:22.670 --> 39:23.730
哪怕只挪了一块碎砖
every shift in the bricks,

39:23.730 --> 39:26.570
我都想  "会引爆炸弹吧"
I think, "this will set it off."

39:29.670 --> 39:34.020
我们等托尼·斯塔克杀我们  等了两天
We wait for two days for Tony Stark to kill us.

39:35.920 --> 39:37.230
我知道他们什么样
I know what they are.

39:38.970 --> 39:43.090
我还好奇  斯托克的实验怎么就你们两个幸存者
I wondered why only you two survived Strucker's experiments.

39:43.650 --> 39:44.890
现在明白了
Now I don't.

39:45.370 --> 39:46.920
我们会讨回正义
We will make it right.

39:47.400 --> 39:49.340
我们是可以伤到他们
You and I can hurt them.

39:50.270 --> 39:53.900
但你可以从内部
But you will tear them apart

39:55.670 --> 39:57.310
把他们瓦解
from the inside.

40:03.940 --> 40:05.170
全世界都有他的足迹
He's all over the globe.

40:05.170 --> 40:08.500
机器人实验室  武器库  喷气动力实验室
Robotics labs, weapons facilities, jet propulsion labs.

40:08.540 --> 40:12.820
都说有金属人  有时候好多个  过去清空了他们那里
Reports of a metal man, or men, coming in and emptying the place.

40:12.900 --> 40:13.900
伤亡呢
Fatalities?

40:13.980 --> 40:15.280
不交火的话没有
Only when engaged.

40:15.280 --> 40:17.050
他们都变得神情恍惚
Mostly guys left in a fugue state

40:17.060 --> 40:19.510
说着什么回忆  最深处的恐惧
going on about old memories, worst fears,

40:19.510 --> 40:21.510
还有东西"快到看不见"
and "something too fast to see."

40:21.820 --> 40:23.020
马克西莫夫兄妹
Maximoffs.

40:23.450 --> 40:26.140
难怪他会找他们  他们都认识同一个人
That makes sense he'd go to them. They have someone in common.

40:26.200 --> 40:27.330
已经不在了
Not anymore.

40:29.700 --> 40:31.990
<b>和平</b>

40:32.040 --> 40:34.240
不行  我向你汇报
That's a negative. I answer to you.

40:35.470 --> 40:36.370
遵命
Yes, ma'am.

40:36.420 --> 40:38.410
巴顿  好像有线索了
Barton. Might have something.

40:38.910 --> 40:39.660
得挂了
I gotta go.

40:39.900 --> 40:40.710
谁啊
Who was that?

40:41.860 --> 40:42.700
女朋友
Girlfriend.

40:45.900 --> 40:46.660
这是什么
What's this?

40:47.200 --> 40:49.780
信息  奥创杀了斯托克
A message. Ultron killed Strucker.

40:50.850 --> 40:53.860
还涂了个鸦  专为我们呢
And he did a Banksy at the crime scene, just for us.

40:53.860 --> 40:55.430
这是烟幕弹
This is a smoke screen.

40:55.510 --> 40:57.540
能直说为什么还要这样做
Why send a message when you've just given a speech?

40:57.540 --> 41:00.420
斯托克有情报  奥创不想让我们知道
Strucker knew something that Ultron wanted us to miss.

41:00.420 --> 41:02.560
是啊  他应该...没错
Yeah, I bet he... Yeah.

41:02.760 --> 41:04.810
有关斯托克的文件都被删除了
Everything we had on Strucker's been erased.

41:05.040 --> 41:06.090
并没有
Not everything.

41:07.730 --> 41:09.130
已知同伙
Known associates.

41:10.040 --> 41:11.580
斯托克男爵有好多朋友啊
Baron Strucker had a lot of friends.

41:11.580 --> 41:13.350
这群人都好可怕
Well, these people are all horrible.

41:13.350 --> 41:15.430
等等  我认识他
Wait. I know that guy.

41:17.530 --> 41:19.660
他一直在非洲沿岸做生意
From back in the day. He operates off the African coast.

41:19.670 --> 41:20.900
黑市军火商
Black market arms.

41:21.450 --> 41:23.690
交集是难免的  同行免不了见面
There are conventions. All right? You meet people.

41:23.690 --> 41:24.950
我没卖过他东西
I didn't sell him anything.

41:25.790 --> 41:27.930
他说了要找什么新的  改变世界的东西
He was talking about finding something new, a game-changer.

41:27.940 --> 41:29.700
搞得跟以色列王似的
It was all very Ahab.

41:30.030 --> 41:30.730
这是什么
This?

41:30.750 --> 41:32.480
是个纹身  之前好像没有
It's a tattoo, I don't think he had it.

41:32.490 --> 41:34.860
那些是纹身  这是烙印
Those are tattoos, this is a brand.

41:36.420 --> 41:40.430
是非洲土著语  意思是贼
Yeah. It's a word in an African dialect meaning "thief."

41:40.430 --> 41:42.200
而且很有侮辱性
In a much less friendly way.

41:42.200 --> 41:43.970
-什么土著语  -瓦坎纳达
- What dialect? - Wakanada.

41:43.970 --> 41:46.190
瓦坎达
Wakanda.

41:47.200 --> 41:49.680
如果他从瓦坎达带了什么东西出来...
If this guy got out of Wakanda with some of their trade goods...

41:49.680 --> 41:51.460
你父亲不是都拿走了吗
I thought your father said he got the last of it.

41:51.460 --> 41:53.900
没明白  从瓦坎达拿走了什么
I don't follow. What comes out of Wakanda?

41:55.970 --> 41:57.450
世界上最坚固的金属
The strongest metal on Earth.

41:59.280 --> 42:00.590
他现在在哪
Where is this guy now?

42:02.580 --> 42:06.920
废船厂

42:04.160 --> 42:06.920
非洲海岸

42:26.120 --> 42:28.000
别跟我说你被手下骗了
Don't tell me your men swindled you.

42:28.000 --> 42:30.050
我给了你六枚
I sent you six short-range

42:30.050 --> 42:32.530
短程热感导弹  你给我一船废铁
heat-seekers and got a boat full of rusted parts.

42:33.160 --> 42:34.550
你得补偿我
Now, you will make it right,

42:34.550 --> 42:37.980
不然再送你枚灰在天上的导弹
or the next missile I send you will come very much faster.

42:39.760 --> 42:43.020
好了  部长  说到哪了
Now, minister, where were we?

43:13.970 --> 43:16.930
能力增强者
Yeah. The Enhanced.

43:17.380 --> 43:19.430
斯托克的好学生
Strucker's prize pupils.

43:22.100 --> 43:23.300
要吃糖吗
Do you want a candy?

43:25.300 --> 43:27.510
斯托克死了真遗憾
I was sorry to hear about Strucker.

43:28.130 --> 43:31.490
不过他也知道自己想把世界变成什么样
But then, he knew what kind of world he was helping create.

43:31.760 --> 43:34.220
人类啊  没什么前途的
Human life. Not a growth market.

43:36.670 --> 43:38.010
你不知道吗
You didn't know?

43:38.680 --> 43:42.310
这是你们第一次威胁别人吗
Is this your first time intimidating someone?

43:42.570 --> 43:45.360
恐怕我没那么怕
I'm afraid I'm not that afraid.

43:45.360 --> 43:47.740
人人都有恐惧的东西
Everybody is afraid of something.

43:47.740 --> 43:48.830
墨鱼
Cuttlefish.

43:50.180 --> 43:51.560
深海动物
Deep sea fish.

43:51.560 --> 43:53.730
会用光  迷幻的光
They make lights, disco lights...

43:54.740 --> 43:57.020
迷惑猎物  然后...
...to hypnotize their prey, and then...

43:58.030 --> 44:00.050
我看了纪录片  可恐怖了
I saw a documentary. It was terrifying.

44:05.640 --> 44:07.870
如果你要鼓捣我的意识
So if you're going to fiddle with my brain

44:09.160 --> 44:11.400
让我看见大墨鱼
and make me see a giant cuttlefish,

44:11.730 --> 44:13.770
我就知道你不是来做生意的
then I know you don't do business.

44:13.770 --> 44:16.120
我也知道你说了不算
And I know you're not in charge.

44:16.120 --> 44:17.840
我只跟
And I only deal

44:18.710 --> 44:20.390
说了算的人打交道
with the man in charge.

44:25.280 --> 44:27.840
说了算的不是人
There is no man in charge.

44:30.760 --> 44:32.280
来谈生意吧
Let's talk business.

44:45.530 --> 44:48.820
《马太福音》16:18

44:45.530 --> 44:48.820
我在这块磐石上  建立我的教会
Upon this rock, I will build my church.

44:50.560 --> 44:51.840
振金
Vibranium.

44:53.060 --> 44:53.780
告诉你
You know,

44:54.200 --> 44:57.260
这东西代价可不小
it came at great personal cost.

44:57.720 --> 44:59.210
值几十亿
It's worth billions.

45:03.680 --> 45:05.040
你也是了
Now so are you.

45:05.930 --> 45:07.900
传到你的假账户里了
It's all under your dummy holdings.

45:07.900 --> 45:10.250
金融真是奇怪
Finance is so weird.

45:11.300 --> 45:12.380
但我总是说
But I always say,

45:12.380 --> 45:14.620
"要让朋友敌人一起富
"Keep your friends rich and your enemies rich

45:13.350 --> 45:15.400
<b>电汇完成</b>

45:14.630 --> 45:17.260
"是敌是友自然分清楚"
"And wait to find out which is which."

45:19.640 --> 45:20.530
斯塔克
Stark.

45:22.030 --> 45:22.840
什么
What?

45:23.140 --> 45:25.270
托尼·斯塔克说过这个
Tony Stark used to say that.

45:26.480 --> 45:27.290
对我说的
To me.

45:28.530 --> 45:29.780
你是他手下
You're one of his.

45:29.860 --> 45:31.810
什么  我不是...
What? I'm not...

45:33.740 --> 45:35.030
我不是
I'm not.

45:35.090 --> 45:36.810
你以为我是斯塔克的傀儡吗
You think I'm one of Stark's puppets?

45:36.810 --> 45:38.390
全听他吩咐
His hollow men?

45:38.390 --> 45:40.640
看看我  我长得像钢铁侠吗
I mean, look at me. Do I look like Iron Man?

45:40.640 --> 45:42.200
斯塔克算什么
Stark is nothing!

45:43.750 --> 45:45.270
真是抱歉  我...
I'm sorry. I'm...

45:46.120 --> 45:48.330
一会就没事了  真是抱歉
I'm sure that's gonna be okay. I'm sorry.

45:48.330 --> 45:49.980
我就是不明白
It's just that I don't understand.

45:49.980 --> 45:53.050
别拿我跟斯塔克比
Don't compare me with Stark!

45:54.850 --> 45:56.010
我在意这个
It's a thing with me.

45:56.010 --> 45:58.250
斯塔克...  就是顽疾
Stark is... He's a sickness!

45:58.550 --> 45:59.390
小子
Junior.

46:01.850 --> 46:03.840
你真要把老爹的心伤得稀碎
You're gonna break your old man's heart.

46:04.850 --> 46:06.210
如果有必要的话
If I have to.

46:07.940 --> 46:09.610
谁也不用打碎东西
Nobody has to break anything.

46:09.620 --> 46:11.650
没做过鸡蛋饼吧
Clearly you've never made an omelet.

46:11.670 --> 46:13.400
这句都到我嘴边了
He beat me by one second.

46:13.780 --> 46:15.520
还真是幽默
Yes. He's funny.

46:15.660 --> 46:16.790
斯塔克先生
Mr. Stark.

46:17.820 --> 46:19.300
感觉亲切吗
It's what? Comfortable?

46:21.130 --> 46:22.390
就像以前一样
Like old times?

46:22.390 --> 46:23.620
我以前可没这样过
This was never my life.

46:23.620 --> 46:25.190
你们俩没必要蹚这浑水
You two can still walk away from this.

46:25.190 --> 46:26.500
不  现在有必要
No, we will.

46:26.580 --> 46:27.800
我知道你们受过苦
I know you've suffered.

46:28.850 --> 46:30.520
美国队长
Captain America.

46:30.850 --> 46:33.170
上帝的正义之子
God's righteous man.

46:33.510 --> 46:36.500
假装自己不是战争机器
Pretending you could live without a war.

46:36.630 --> 46:39.420
我要是人类的话早吐了
I can't physically throw up in my mouth, but...

46:39.420 --> 46:42.040
你要是相信和平  就不要打破它
If you believe in peace, then let us keep it.

46:42.040 --> 46:45.310
你混淆了"和平"与"安宁"的概念
I think you're confusing "peace" with "quiet."

46:45.580 --> 46:47.530
你要振金做什么
What's the vibranium for?

46:47.610 --> 46:48.860
你终于开口问了
I'm glad you asked that,

46:48.860 --> 46:52.960
让我给你们解释下我邪恶的计划
because I wanted to take this time to explain my evil plan.

47:12.330 --> 47:14.130
-开火  -朝谁
- Shoot them. - Which ones?

47:14.130 --> 47:15.420
所有人
All of them!

47:15.420 --> 47:16.670
上上上
Move! Move! Move!

48:05.610 --> 48:06.900
待着吧  孩子
Stay down, kid.

48:09.310 --> 48:11.840
该玩玩他们的意识了
It's time for some mind games.

48:13.000 --> 48:15.650
各位  需要我变绿吗
Guys? Is this a code green?

48:31.210 --> 48:32.760
托尔  什么情况
Thor, status.

48:32.860 --> 48:34.910
那小姑娘想扰乱我的心智
The girl tried to warp my mind.

48:34.960 --> 48:37.800
小心了  凡人恐怕挡不住她的意识控制
Take special care. I doubt a human could keep her at bay.

48:38.450 --> 48:41.320
幸好  我是神
Fortunately, I am mighty.

49:01.240 --> 49:03.310
这进展得太顺利了
This is going very well.

49:15.070 --> 49:16.730
精神控制什么的我早就尝过了
I've done the whole mind control thing.

49:17.760 --> 49:18.670
真不感兴趣
Not a fan.

49:25.920 --> 49:27.460
别让我逮着你
Yeah, you better run.

49:29.600 --> 49:31.770
活着的  得行动了
Who's ever standing, we got to move!

49:33.360 --> 49:34.260
各位
Guys?

49:52.550 --> 49:53.390
再来
Again.

49:53.890 --> 49:55.050
她们会撑不住的
You'll break them.

49:55.630 --> 49:57.470
撑不下来的是活该
Only the breakable ones.

49:57.900 --> 49:59.340
而你坚若磐石
You're made of marble.

49:59.710 --> 50:02.530
毕业典礼后我们再庆祝
We'll celebrate after the graduation ceremony.

50:02.880 --> 50:04.190
如果我失败了呢
What if I fail?

50:09.480 --> 50:10.820
你从不失败
You never fail.

50:33.690 --> 50:35.570
准备好跟我共舞了吗
Are you ready for our dance?

50:44.930 --> 50:45.990
是他吗
Is it him?

50:46.200 --> 50:48.210
是奥丁的长子吗
Is that the first son of Odin?

50:48.820 --> 50:50.200
海姆达尔  你的眼睛
Heimdall, your eyes.

50:50.760 --> 50:52.710
它们看清了一切
They see everything.

50:53.140 --> 50:55.910
看到你带领我们走向冥府
They see you leading us to Hel.

50:56.260 --> 50:57.290
醒醒
Wake up!

51:00.680 --> 51:02.590
战争结束了  史蒂夫
The war is over, Steve.

51:03.110 --> 51:04.560
我们可以回家了
We can go home.

51:06.130 --> 51:07.300
想想看
Imagine it.

51:16.520 --> 51:18.610
我还能拯救你
I can still save you!

51:18.610 --> 51:21.740
我们都死了  你看不到吗
We're all dead! Can you not see?

51:26.500 --> 51:29.130
你是毁灭者  奥丁森
You're a destroyer, Odinson.

51:31.950 --> 51:34.710
看看你的神力干了什么
See where your power leads.

51:44.950 --> 51:46.030
太大意了
Sloppy.

51:46.960 --> 51:48.340
你是故意失败吗
Pretending to fail.

51:49.790 --> 51:51.880
必须通过毕业典礼
The ceremony is necessary

51:52.520 --> 51:54.870
你才能立足在世界上
for you to take your place in the world.

51:55.060 --> 51:56.790
我没有地方可以立足
I have no place in the world.

51:56.790 --> 51:58.020
没错
Exactly.

52:03.200 --> 52:05.260
-我该怎么办  -好疼
- What can I do? - It hurts.

52:06.500 --> 52:07.420
我去杀了他
I'm going to kill him.

52:07.420 --> 52:08.430
-马上回来  -不
- I'll be right back. - No.

52:08.890 --> 52:10.040
我没事
I'm all right.

52:11.100 --> 52:16.840
我要...我要完成计划
I want... I want to finish the plan.

52:17.700 --> 52:19.310
搞定那个大家伙
I want the big one.

52:30.410 --> 52:32.450
振金被运走了哦
The vibranium is getting away.

52:33.050 --> 52:34.250
你哪也别想去
And you're not going anywhere.

52:34.250 --> 52:37.210
不需要  我已经无处不在了
Of course not. I'm already there.

52:37.400 --> 52:38.430
你会明白的
You'll catch on.

52:38.430 --> 52:41.440
但首先你得搞定班纳博士
But first, you might need to catch Dr. Banner.

52:55.510 --> 52:57.690
搜索新闻视频  关键词"绿巨人"
News or footage. Keyword, "Hulk."

53:01.960 --> 53:04.200
娜塔莎  你得过来唱摇篮曲了
Natasha, I could really use a lullaby.

53:04.430 --> 53:07.080
不行  这一阵她是不行了
That's not gonna happen. Not for a while.

53:07.810 --> 53:09.180
大伙都倒下了
The whole team is down.

53:10.170 --> 53:11.640
现在没人能支援你了
You got no backup here.

53:12.700 --> 53:13.930
那我呼叫维罗妮卡
I'm calling in Veronica.

53:25.230 --> 53:26.420
我们需要支援
We need backup!

54:05.750 --> 54:07.680
离开这  快走
Go! Keep moving!

54:46.580 --> 54:48.960
好了  所有人退后
All right, everybody, stand down!

54:55.020 --> 54:56.030
听我一句行吗
Will you listen to me?

54:56.790 --> 54:58.990
那个小女巫搞乱了你的头脑
That little witch is messing with your mind.

54:59.250 --> 55:01.520
你比她更强  也更聪明
You're stronger than her. You're smarter than her.

55:01.520 --> 55:03.130
你可是布鲁斯·班纳啊
You're Bruce Banner.

55:03.440 --> 55:05.490
我错了  我错了  不能提小班纳
Right, right, right, don't mention puny Banner.

55:10.530 --> 55:11.350
好吧
Okay!

55:33.080 --> 55:34.670
背后偷袭
In the back?

55:34.760 --> 55:36.050
太阴险了  班纳
Dick move, Banner.

55:47.630 --> 55:49.020
维罗妮卡  搭把手
Veronica, give me a hand.

56:16.330 --> 56:18.160
听话  听话  快睡觉
Go to sleep, go to sleep, go to sleep.

56:27.620 --> 56:29.610
好吧  伙计  先把你弄出城
Okay, pal, we're gonna get you out of town.

56:31.470 --> 56:32.880
别去那边  别去那边
Not that way, not that way.

56:41.140 --> 56:43.540
拜托  布鲁斯  配合一下
Come on, Bruce! You gotta work with me.

56:56.890 --> 56:58.030
所有人都出去
Everybody, out!

57:04.440 --> 57:05.580
下去了
Going down?

57:15.300 --> 57:16.130
对不起
I'm sorry.

57:30.690 --> 57:31.860
损伤报告
Damage report?

57:32.560 --> 57:35.090
真直白  再运点零件来
That's comprehensive. Show me something.

57:43.520 --> 57:44.730
搜索生命迹象

57:44.730 --> 57:45.230
无人员在内

57:45.230 --> 57:46.350
安全

57:46.640 --> 57:48.260
买下这栋楼最快得多久
How quickly can we buy this building?

58:20.570 --> 58:22.280
-行动  行动  行动  -上上上
- Move! Move! Move! - Go, go, go!

58:25.520 --> 58:26.840
去侧翼  去侧翼
Flank him, flank him!

59:16.350 --> 59:18.530
电视台可喜欢报道你们了呢
The news is loving you guys.

59:19.420 --> 59:20.850
但大家都不喜欢
Nobody else is.

59:21.430 --> 59:23.830
警方还没发布班纳的逮捕令
There's been no official call for Banner's arrest

59:23.830 --> 59:25.710
但消息已经传开了
but it's in the air.

59:26.360 --> 59:27.460
斯塔克救援基金呢
The Stark Relief Foundation?

59:27.460 --> 59:28.780
已经在现场了
Already on the scene.

59:28.840 --> 59:30.020
团队怎么样
How's the team?

59:30.160 --> 59:31.210
大家都...
Everyone's...

59:32.330 --> 59:35.180
我们受了重创  不过会好的
We took a hit. We'll shake it off.

59:35.240 --> 59:39.310
现在最好一直潜伏  别再回来
Well, for now, I'd stay in stealth mode and stay away from here.

59:40.350 --> 59:41.760
就是逃走藏起来
So, run and hide?

59:42.460 --> 59:44.220
找不到奥创
Until we can find Ultron,

59:44.220 --> 59:46.710
我也没什么好办法
I don't have a lot else to offer.

59:47.760 --> 59:48.650
我们也没有
Neither do we.

59:55.780 --> 59:57.100
要换班吗
Hey, you wanna switch out?

59:57.640 --> 59:58.570
我没事
No, I'm good.

59:59.270 --> 01:00:01.360
你要是想睡觉  最好趁现在
If you wanna get some kip, now's a good time

01:00:01.360 --> 01:00:02.690
还有几个小时才到呢
because we're still a few hours out.

01:00:02.990 --> 01:00:05.090
到哪
Few hours from where?

01:00:05.670 --> 01:00:06.920
安全屋
A safe house.

01:00:33.230 --> 01:00:34.510
这是什么地方
What is this place?

01:00:34.750 --> 01:00:35.700
安全屋
Safe house.

01:00:36.900 --> 01:00:37.820
但愿吧
Let's hope.

01:00:43.330 --> 01:00:44.120
亲爱的
Honey?

01:00:45.060 --> 01:00:45.830
我到家了
I'm home.

01:00:48.970 --> 01:00:49.720
你好
Hi.

01:00:50.120 --> 01:00:51.020
还有朋友
Company.

01:00:51.130 --> 01:00:53.030
抱歉没提前打电话
Sorry, didn't call ahead.

01:00:54.150 --> 01:00:55.710
他绝对是个什么特工
This is an agent of some kind.

01:00:55.740 --> 01:00:57.920
各位  这是劳拉
Gentlemen, this is Laura.

01:00:59.230 --> 01:01:01.050
你们我全都知道
I know all of your names.

01:01:04.220 --> 01:01:05.060
来了
Incoming.

01:01:05.740 --> 01:01:07.600
-爸爸  -宝贝们
- Dad! - Hi, sweetheart!

01:01:07.600 --> 01:01:08.540
小伙子
Hey, buddy.

01:01:08.540 --> 01:01:10.210
你们好吗
How are you guys doing?

01:01:10.480 --> 01:01:12.880
-这些是小特工  -看你的脸
- These are smaller agents. - Look at your face!

01:01:12.880 --> 01:01:14.120
我的天
Oh, my goodness.

01:01:14.130 --> 01:01:15.970
小娜阿姨来了吗
Did you bring Auntie Nat?

01:01:16.640 --> 01:01:19.390
来抱一个看来没来
Why don't you hug her and find out?

01:01:20.730 --> 01:01:21.920
抱歉打扰你们了
Sorry for barging in on you.

01:01:21.920 --> 01:01:22.880
是啊  本来想提前打电话的
Yeah, we would have called ahead,

01:01:22.880 --> 01:01:25.230
但我们根本不知道你们的存在
but we were busy having no idea that you existed.

01:01:25.230 --> 01:01:27.960
我加入神盾局的时候弗瑞帮我安排的
Yeah, well, Fury helped me set this up when I joined.

01:01:29.060 --> 01:01:30.470
这里没有进神盾局的档案
He kept it off S.H.I.E.L.D.'s files.

01:01:30.470 --> 01:01:31.630
以后最好也不要
I'd like to keep it that way.

01:01:32.470 --> 01:01:34.470
这地方挺适合暂时藏身的
I figure it's a good place to lay low.

01:01:34.700 --> 01:01:35.710
亲爱的
Honey.

01:01:36.570 --> 01:01:37.840
我好想你
I missed you.

01:01:38.100 --> 01:01:39.640
小娜塔莎怎么样
How's little Natasha?

01:01:39.640 --> 01:01:40.810
她是...
She's...

01:01:42.770 --> 01:01:44.360
内特尼尔[男名]
Nathaniel.

01:01:47.040 --> 01:01:48.150
叛徒
Traitor.

01:02:03.730 --> 01:02:04.490
托尔
Thor?

01:02:04.760 --> 01:02:06.850
我在梦里看到了什么
I saw something in that dream.

01:02:06.850 --> 01:02:09.530
我需要找答案  这里找不到
I need answers. I won't find them here.

01:02:20.310 --> 01:02:21.350
我们可以回家了
We can go home.

01:02:32.920 --> 01:02:34.600
你都是瞎担心
See? You worried for nothing.

01:02:34.840 --> 01:02:36.790
我是感觉不出来  你呢
Can't even feel the difference, can you?

01:02:39.380 --> 01:02:40.640
他们要是住这的话
If they're sleeping here,

01:02:40.640 --> 01:02:42.360
有的人就得挤一挤了
some of them are gonna have to double up.

01:02:44.580 --> 01:02:46.430
他们肯定不愿意
Yeah, that's not gonna sell.

01:02:49.600 --> 01:02:51.730
小娜和班纳博士怎么回事
What about Nat and Dr. Banner?

01:02:52.320 --> 01:02:53.910
她俩有多久了
How long has that been going on?

01:02:54.830 --> 01:02:55.680
什么多久
Has what?

01:02:56.930 --> 01:02:58.630
你真可爱
You are so cute.

01:02:59.070 --> 01:03:00.900
小娜和班纳
Nat and Banner?

01:03:01.020 --> 01:03:02.830
等你长大了再跟你解释
I'll explain when you're older,

01:03:02.830 --> 01:03:03.680
鹰眼
Hawkeye.

01:03:03.680 --> 01:03:05.250
好吧
Well, okay.

01:03:07.420 --> 01:03:08.640
情况不妙吧
It's bad, right?

01:03:08.940 --> 01:03:10.720
小娜好像很受伤
Nat seems really shaken.

01:03:11.640 --> 01:03:13.300
奥创有两个盟友
Ultron has these allies.

01:03:13.310 --> 01:03:16.860
两个孩子  都是小流氓
These kids. They're punks, really.

01:03:18.990 --> 01:03:20.780
他们拿了根特别大的棍子
But they carry a big, damn stick.

01:03:21.560 --> 01:03:23.120
小娜挨了挺重的一下
And Nat took a serious hit.

01:03:23.910 --> 01:03:25.960
得有人教训教训他们
Someone's gonna have to teach them some manners.

01:03:26.780 --> 01:03:28.260
那个人就是你吗
That someone being you.

01:03:29.830 --> 01:03:32.370
你当复仇者我非常支持
You know I totally support your Avenging.

01:03:32.670 --> 01:03:34.480
我无比自豪
I couldn't be prouder.

01:03:36.130 --> 01:03:37.790
但我看到他们...
But I see those guys...

01:03:37.790 --> 01:03:40.020
神一样的...
Those gods...

01:03:41.510 --> 01:03:42.930
你觉得他们不需要我
You don't think they need me.

01:03:43.890 --> 01:03:47.600
我觉得他们需要  这样更可怕
I think they do, which is a lot scarier.

01:03:48.900 --> 01:03:50.070
他们问题真是多啊
They're a mess.

01:03:51.650 --> 01:03:52.440
是啊
Yeah.

01:03:53.440 --> 01:03:55.030
那也是我的问题
I guess they're my mess.

01:03:56.400 --> 01:03:57.670
你得确保
You need to be sure

01:03:58.350 --> 01:04:00.500
团队能合作下去
that this team is really a team,

01:04:00.810 --> 01:04:02.400
能时刻支持你
and that they have your back.

01:04:06.230 --> 01:04:08.070
我们的日子也要变了
Things are changing for us.

01:04:08.850 --> 01:04:10.800
再过几个月
In a few months' time,

01:04:11.350 --> 01:04:13.730
孩子就要比大人多了
you and me are gonna be outnumbered.

01:04:14.340 --> 01:04:15.570
我得...
I need...

01:04:18.820 --> 01:04:20.370
一定要确保
Just be sure.

01:04:21.600 --> 01:04:22.380
遵命
Yes, ma'am.

01:04:32.000 --> 01:04:33.910
我能感觉到不一样
I can feel the difference.

01:04:36.180 --> 01:04:40.890
尤金基因实验室

01:04:37.510 --> 01:04:40.890
韩国  首尔

01:04:46.920 --> 01:04:49.720
敢出声  你的员工都得死
Scream, and your entire staff dies.

01:04:51.530 --> 01:04:54.010
我本可以杀了你  海伦  刚见面那晚
I could've killed you, Helen, the night we met.

01:04:54.010 --> 01:04:55.110
但我没有
I didn't.

01:04:55.120 --> 01:04:56.640
是要我谢你吗
Do you expect a thank-you note?

01:04:56.640 --> 01:04:58.370
我要你知道为什么
I expect you to know why.

01:05:00.520 --> 01:05:01.250
再生摇篮
The Cradle.

01:05:01.250 --> 01:05:03.220
这就是未来  托尼
This is the next thing, Tony.

01:05:03.390 --> 01:05:06.270
这就是未来的我
This is the next me.

01:05:06.700 --> 01:05:09.030
再生摇篮能生成组织
The Regeneration Cradle prints tissue.

01:05:09.610 --> 01:05:11.030
可造不出活的躯体
It can't build a living body.

01:05:11.030 --> 01:05:12.830
可以  你可以
It can. You can.

01:05:12.840 --> 01:05:14.850
你只是缺少材料
You lack the materials.

01:05:16.520 --> 01:05:18.490
你很厉害  海伦
You're a brilliant woman, Helen.

01:05:21.160 --> 01:05:24.440
但大家都有进步的空间
But we all have room to improve.

01:05:45.970 --> 01:05:48.430
我不知道你在等着
I didn't realize you were waiting.

01:05:48.430 --> 01:05:49.420
我想跟你一起洗来着
I would've joined you,

01:05:49.420 --> 01:05:52.820
但是好像时机不太对
but it didn't seem like the right time.

01:05:53.860 --> 01:05:56.030
热水被他们用光了
They used up all the hot water.

01:05:56.700 --> 01:05:57.890
真该跟你一起洗
I should've joined you.

01:05:58.300 --> 01:05:59.520
错过了机会
Missed our window.

01:06:00.780 --> 01:06:01.570
是吗
Did we?

01:06:05.680 --> 01:06:07.470
世界看到了绿巨人
The world just saw the Hulk.

01:06:08.940 --> 01:06:10.850
第一次见到了真正的绿巨人
The real Hulk, for the first time.

01:06:14.570 --> 01:06:15.520
你知道我得离开
You know I have to leave.

01:06:15.520 --> 01:06:17.200
你是觉得我应该留下吗
You assume that I have to stay?

01:06:19.230 --> 01:06:21.900
我做了个梦
I had this dream.

01:06:22.330 --> 01:06:24.400
做梦的时候觉得挺正常
The kind that seems normal at the time,

01:06:25.260 --> 01:06:26.450
但等醒了...
but when you wake...

01:06:26.880 --> 01:06:27.940
你梦见什么了
What did you dream?

01:06:29.410 --> 01:06:30.780
我是复仇者
That I was an Avenger.

01:06:32.700 --> 01:06:36.770
不只是他们一手打造的刺客
That I was anything more than the assassin they made me.

01:06:38.540 --> 01:06:40.450
你对自己太狠[硬]了
I think you're being hard on yourself.

01:06:42.610 --> 01:06:44.720
这不是你该干的吗
Here I was hoping that was your job.

01:06:48.130 --> 01:06:49.340
你干什么
What are you doing?

01:06:51.260 --> 01:06:52.820
顺其自然
I'm running with it.

01:06:54.270 --> 01:06:55.330
和你一起
With you.

01:06:56.620 --> 01:06:58.900
如果你打算走
If running is the plan,

01:07:00.080 --> 01:07:01.540
想去哪去哪
as far as you want.

01:07:03.980 --> 01:07:05.770
你疯了吗
Are you out of your mind?

01:07:11.020 --> 01:07:12.450
我希望你明白...
I want you to understand that...

01:07:12.460 --> 01:07:13.460
娜塔莎
Natasha,

01:07:14.980 --> 01:07:16.150
我能去哪
where can I go?

01:07:17.570 --> 01:07:19.620
我到哪不是个祸害
Where in the world am I not a threat?

01:07:19.620 --> 01:07:21.860
-在我这不是  -你确定吗
- You're not a threat to me. - Are you sure?

01:07:22.820 --> 01:07:24.360
哪怕我没...
Even if I didn't just...

01:07:26.580 --> 01:07:28.260
跟着我没有未来的
There's no future with me.

01:07:29.770 --> 01:07:31.290
我不能...
I can't ever...

01:07:31.530 --> 01:07:33.320
我不可能这样
I can't have this.

01:07:33.800 --> 01:07:34.800
有孩子
Kids.

01:07:35.580 --> 01:07:37.820
你自己想想  我是真的不能
Do the math. I physically can't.

01:07:39.670 --> 01:07:40.940
我也不能
Neither can I.

01:07:45.900 --> 01:07:49.340
我受训的那个红屋子里...
In the Red Room where I was trained...

01:07:49.900 --> 01:07:51.410
我长大的地方
where I was raised,

01:07:53.520 --> 01:07:55.860
有个毕业典礼
they have a graduation ceremony.

01:07:57.760 --> 01:07:59.300
就是做绝育
They sterilize you.

01:08:02.710 --> 01:08:03.880
效果很好
It's efficient.

01:08:07.040 --> 01:08:08.560
少了件操心的事
One less thing to worry about.

01:08:10.550 --> 01:08:13.520
唯一一件可能比任务还重要的事
The one thing that might matter more than a mission.

01:08:16.400 --> 01:08:18.000
一切都简单多了
Makes everything easier.

01:08:19.490 --> 01:08:20.630
哪怕是杀人
Even killing.

01:08:25.760 --> 01:08:28.210
你还以为队伍里就你一个怪物吗
You still think you're the only monster on the team?

01:08:35.120 --> 01:08:36.680
我们一起隐居吗
So, we disappear?

01:08:43.770 --> 01:08:45.780
托尔没说他去哪找答案了吗
Thor didn't say where he was going for answers?

01:08:46.510 --> 01:08:48.900
我的队员也不总跟我畅所欲言的
Sometimes my teammates don't tell me things.

01:08:49.890 --> 01:08:52.110
我还希望托尔能对我敞开胸襟呢
I was kind of hoping Thor would be the exception.

01:08:52.280 --> 01:08:53.810
给他点时间
Yeah, give him time.

01:08:54.380 --> 01:08:56.370
我们不知道马克西莫夫给他看了什么
We don't know what the Maximoff kid showed him.

01:08:58.200 --> 01:08:59.930
"地球上最强大的英雄组合"
"Earth's mightiest heroes."

01:09:00.270 --> 01:09:02.250
棉花糖一样被拆散了
Pulled us apart like cotton candy.

01:09:02.330 --> 01:09:04.190
你好像没什么大碍嘛
Seems like you walked away all right.

01:09:06.410 --> 01:09:07.370
有问题吗
Is that a problem?

01:09:07.480 --> 01:09:09.380
没有黑暗面的人不值得信任
I don't trust a guy without a dark side.

01:09:10.840 --> 01:09:12.070
就算我老古董吧
Call me old-fashioned.

01:09:12.070 --> 01:09:14.300
那只是你还没见过
Well, let's just say you haven't seen it yet.

01:09:14.810 --> 01:09:16.840
你知道奥创想分裂我们吧
You know Ultron is trying to tear us apart, right?

01:09:17.290 --> 01:09:18.620
你肯定知道
Well, I guess you'd know.

01:09:19.240 --> 01:09:20.830
会不会告诉我们就不一定了
Whether you'd tell us is a bit of a question.

01:09:20.830 --> 01:09:22.110
班纳和我在搞科研
Banner and I were doing research.

01:09:22.110 --> 01:09:24.420
-会对团队有影响  -是会解散团队吧
- That would affect the team. - That would end the team!

01:09:24.820 --> 01:09:26.110
那不正是目的吗
Isn't that the mission?

01:09:26.110 --> 01:09:27.500
不是我们战斗的理由吗
Isn't that the "why we fight"?

01:09:27.500 --> 01:09:29.910
为了结束战斗  为了回家
So we can end the fight. So we get to go home!

01:09:32.980 --> 01:09:35.320
每次有人想在战争开打前取胜
Every time someone tries to win a war before it starts,

01:09:35.320 --> 01:09:38.500
都会牺牲无辜的人  每次都是
innocent people die. Every time.

01:09:40.500 --> 01:09:41.520
真抱歉
I'm sorry.

01:09:42.100 --> 01:09:43.290
斯塔克先生
Mr. Stark...

01:09:43.780 --> 01:09:44.870
克林特说你不会介意的
Clint said you wouldn't mind,

01:09:44.870 --> 01:09:47.490
我家的拖拉机启动不了了
but our tractor doesn't seem to want to start at all.

01:09:47.710 --> 01:09:49.260
-你能不能去...  -没问题  我去看看
- I thought maybe you might... - Yeah, I'll give her a kick.

01:09:53.520 --> 01:09:54.850
别偷我劈的柴
Don't take from my pile.

01:10:05.500 --> 01:10:06.480
好啊亲爱的
Hello, Dear.

01:10:09.440 --> 01:10:10.530
来给我讲讲
Tell me everything.

01:10:12.140 --> 01:10:13.300
哪里不舒服
What ails you?

01:10:13.860 --> 01:10:14.770
行行好
Do me a favor.

01:10:16.610 --> 01:10:18.530
别把它弄活了
Try not to bring it to life.

01:10:18.800 --> 01:10:20.810
巴顿夫人还真是狡猾
Why, Ms. Barton, you little minx.

01:10:20.950 --> 01:10:22.590
我明白了  希尔给你打电话了
I get it. Maria Hill called you, right?

01:10:23.560 --> 01:10:24.830
她有不给你打工的时候吗
Was she ever not working for you?

01:10:24.830 --> 01:10:26.370
人工智能
Artificial intelligence.

01:10:27.470 --> 01:10:29.150
你都没犹豫一下
You never even hesitated.

01:10:29.150 --> 01:10:30.840
今天真的很漫长
Look, it's been a really long day,

01:10:31.110 --> 01:10:32.540
有尤金·奥尼尔的小说[同名]那么长
like Eugene O'Neill long,

01:10:32.550 --> 01:10:35.000
来直接说你能解决什么问题
so how's about we skip to the part where you're useful.

01:10:35.000 --> 01:10:37.630
看着我的眼睛  告诉我你会关闭奥创
Look me in the eye and tell me you're going to shut him down.

01:10:37.630 --> 01:10:38.910
你又不是我的局长
You're not the director of me.

01:10:38.910 --> 01:10:40.820
我谁的局长都不是
I'm not the director of anybody.

01:10:41.350 --> 01:10:42.690
我就是个老头子
I'm just an old man

01:10:43.580 --> 01:10:45.790
刚好很关心你
who cares very much about you.

01:10:48.100 --> 01:10:49.950
我是害死复仇者联盟的人
And I'm the man who killed the Avengers.

01:10:51.620 --> 01:10:52.530
我看到了
I saw it.

01:10:53.140 --> 01:10:55.230
我没告诉大伙  没法说
I didn't tell the team. How could I?

01:10:55.980 --> 01:10:57.990
我看到他们都死了  尼克  我感觉到了
I saw them all dead, Nick. I felt it.

01:10:58.060 --> 01:10:59.490
世界也终结了
The whole world, too.

01:11:00.390 --> 01:11:01.290
因为我
Because of me.

01:11:02.950 --> 01:11:03.780
我没准备好
I wasn't ready.

01:11:05.270 --> 01:11:06.420
我没尽力
I didn't do all I could.

01:11:07.680 --> 01:11:10.120
这是马克西莫夫的把戏  斯塔克
Maximoff girl, she's working you, Stark.

01:11:10.500 --> 01:11:11.480
利用你的恐惧
Playing on your fear.

01:11:11.490 --> 01:11:13.860
不是把戏  我真看到了
I wasn't tricked, I was shown.

01:11:14.000 --> 01:11:15.890
不是噩梦  是我留给后人的
Wasn't a nightmare, it was my legacy.

01:11:16.300 --> 01:11:18.380
我带着大家走向了死亡
The end of the path I started us on.

01:11:19.210 --> 01:11:22.340
你是发明过不少厉害的玩意  托尼
You come up with some pretty impressive inventions, Tony.

01:11:24.030 --> 01:11:25.890
可战争不是
War isn't one of them.

01:11:28.880 --> 01:11:30.360
我看到朋友死去
I watched my friends die.

01:11:30.590 --> 01:11:32.800
你觉得这够惨了吗
You'd think that'd be as bad as it gets, right?

01:11:34.210 --> 01:11:34.990
还不够
Nope.

01:11:36.590 --> 01:11:37.970
那还不是最坏的
It wasn't the worst part.

01:11:38.350 --> 01:11:39.540
最坏的是
The worst part

01:11:40.190 --> 01:11:41.460
只有你没死
is that you didn't.

01:11:48.410 --> 01:11:49.230
今晚见了
I'll see you tonight.

01:11:49.740 --> 01:11:54.160
皇家霍罗威大学

01:11:50.990 --> 01:11:54.160
伦敦

01:11:51.990 --> 01:11:52.930
造型不错
I like the look.

01:11:54.440 --> 01:11:56.880
不过想不惹人注意还差点
If you're going for inconspicuous, though, near miss.

01:11:57.540 --> 01:11:58.480
我需要你帮忙
I need your help.

01:11:58.720 --> 01:11:59.890
有人需要真好
It's nice to be needed.

01:11:59.970 --> 01:12:00.870
很危险
It's dangerous.

01:12:01.840 --> 01:12:03.720
不危险我才失望呢
I'd be disappointed if it wasn't.

01:12:06.620 --> 01:12:09.620
奥创把你们赶走  好给自己争取时间
Ultron took you folks out of play to buy himself time.

01:12:10.280 --> 01:12:13.340
我的线人都说他在打造什么
My contacts all say he's building something.

01:12:13.450 --> 01:12:15.690
他弄了那么多振金
The amount of vibranium he made off with,

01:12:15.690 --> 01:12:17.550
应该不止一件
I don't think it's just one thing.

01:12:17.550 --> 01:12:19.070
那奥创呢
What about Ultron himself?

01:12:19.660 --> 01:12:21.690
他好追踪  哪都有他
He's easy to track. He's everywhere.

01:12:22.040 --> 01:12:24.960
他比母猪还高产
The guy is multiplying faster than a Catholic rabbit.

01:12:25.050 --> 01:12:25.910
可还是看不透
It still doesn't help us

01:12:25.910 --> 01:12:28.040
他究竟在计划什么
get an angle on any of his plans, though.

01:12:28.040 --> 01:12:29.340
还想找核弹密码吗
Is he still going after launch codes?

01:12:29.340 --> 01:12:30.460
是啊
Yes, he is.

01:12:30.460 --> 01:12:32.250
可一直没什么进展
But he's not making any headway.

01:12:32.250 --> 01:12:34.790
我高中玩大冒险就把五角大楼的防火墙破了
I cracked the Pentagon's firewall in high school on a dare.

01:12:34.790 --> 01:12:37.950
我联系了"链结"的朋友
Well, I contacted our friends at the Nexus about that.

01:12:37.950 --> 01:12:38.590
链结
Nexus?

01:12:38.590 --> 01:12:40.490
奥斯陆的互联网中心
It's the world internet hub in Oslo.

01:12:40.490 --> 01:12:42.570
所有联网数据都要经过那里
Every byte of data flows through there.

01:12:42.570 --> 01:12:43.810
全球最快的连接速度
Fastest access on Earth.

01:12:43.810 --> 01:12:44.980
他们怎么说
So, what did they say?

01:12:44.980 --> 01:12:46.600
他认准了核弹
He's fixated on the missiles.

01:12:47.070 --> 01:12:49.180
但密码一直在改
But the codes are constantly being changed.

01:12:49.180 --> 01:12:49.880
谁在改
By whom?

01:12:51.610 --> 01:12:52.760
未知势力
Parties unknown.

01:12:52.760 --> 01:12:53.590
我们有盟友吗
Do we have an ally?

01:12:53.590 --> 01:12:56.850
奥创有个对手  这可不一样
Ultron's got an enemy. That's not the same thing.

01:12:56.850 --> 01:12:58.810
我还是特别想知道幕后是谁
Still, I'd pay folding money to know who it is.

01:12:58.810 --> 01:13:00.340
我得去趟奥斯陆
I might need to visit Oslo.

01:13:00.450 --> 01:13:01.660
寻找未知势力
Find our unknown.

01:13:01.660 --> 01:13:03.160
跟你重聚很开心  老大
Well, this is good times, boss,

01:13:03.160 --> 01:13:04.540
但我本希望你这次来
but I was kind of hoping when I saw you,

01:13:04.540 --> 01:13:05.900
你能多带点什么来
you'd have more than that.

01:13:05.900 --> 01:13:07.920
我还有你们啊
I do. I have you.

01:13:08.810 --> 01:13:12.410
过去遍地都是我的眼线  哪都不放过
Back in the day, I had eyes everywhere. Ears, everywhere else.

01:13:12.490 --> 01:13:15.540
你们手里什么高科技都有
You kids had all the tech you could dream up.

01:13:16.250 --> 01:13:18.110
可是现在  大伙回到了地球上
Here we all are, back on Earth,

01:13:18.570 --> 01:13:22.640
只能靠自己的智慧和意志拯救世界
with nothing but our wit and our will to save the world.

01:13:23.760 --> 01:13:26.080
奥创说阻止他实现目的的
Ultron says the Avengers are the only thing

01:13:26.080 --> 01:13:28.030
就只有复仇者联盟了
between him and his mission.

01:13:28.110 --> 01:13:29.900
不管他承不承认
And whether or not he admits it,

01:13:29.900 --> 01:13:33.550
他的任务都是毁灭全球
his mission is global destruction.

01:13:33.810 --> 01:13:36.640
这一切  都将入土
All this, laid in a grave.

01:13:38.160 --> 01:13:39.280
站出来吧
So stand.

01:13:40.640 --> 01:13:42.480
战胜那个金属王八蛋
Outwit the platinum bastard.

01:13:42.850 --> 01:13:44.810
史蒂夫不喜欢你这么说
Steve doesn't like that kind of talk.

01:13:44.810 --> 01:13:46.300
告诉你  罗曼诺夫
You know what, Romanoff?

01:13:46.750 --> 01:13:48.640
他想要什么
So, what does he want?

01:13:49.870 --> 01:13:51.120
变得更好
To become better.

01:13:51.810 --> 01:13:52.940
比我们都好
Better than us.

01:13:53.490 --> 01:13:54.980
他一直在造身体
He keeps building bodies.

01:13:54.980 --> 01:13:56.130
人的身体
Person bodies.

01:13:56.420 --> 01:13:57.890
人类的性能太差
The human form is inefficient.

01:13:57.890 --> 01:14:00.000
生物角度上讲  我们被被淘汰了
Biologically speaking, we're outmoded.

01:14:00.030 --> 01:14:02.270
可他还总要回来找我们
But he keeps coming back to it.

01:14:02.510 --> 01:14:04.960
你们两个设定要他保护人类时
When you two programmed him to protect the human race,

01:14:04.960 --> 01:14:06.380
真是失败得一塌糊涂
you amazingly failed.

01:14:06.380 --> 01:14:08.270
他们不需要保护
They don't need to be protected.

01:14:08.880 --> 01:14:10.370
需要进化
They need to evolve.

01:14:12.670 --> 01:14:14.530
奥创要进化
Ultron's going to evolve.

01:14:14.860 --> 01:14:15.650
怎么进化
How?

01:14:17.260 --> 01:14:19.740
有人联系过海伦·赵吗
Has anyone been in contact with Helen Cho?

01:14:23.930 --> 01:14:24.910
真美
It's beautiful.

01:14:25.710 --> 01:14:28.750
振金原子不仅能跟组织共存
The vibranium atoms aren't just compatible with the tissue cells,

01:14:28.750 --> 01:14:30.270
还结合了起来
they're binding them.

01:14:30.540 --> 01:14:32.070
神盾局居然从没想过...
And S.H.I.E.L.D. Never even thought to...

01:14:32.070 --> 01:14:34.620
地球上功能最多的材料
The most versatile substance on the planet,

01:14:34.670 --> 01:14:36.700
居然用它做飞盘
and they used it to make a Frisbee.

01:14:37.240 --> 01:14:38.730
人类就是这样
Typical of humans.

01:14:38.730 --> 01:14:41.630
研究一点就浅尝辄止
They scratch the surface and never think

01:14:43.220 --> 01:14:44.480
不想深入
to look within.

01:14:55.190 --> 01:14:56.780
我带娜塔莎和克林特
I'll take Natasha and Clint.

01:14:56.780 --> 01:14:58.920
好  只是侦查  我先去链接
All right. Strictly recon. I'll hit the Nexus.

01:14:58.920 --> 01:15:00.190
办完就找你们
I'll join you as soon as I can.

01:15:00.190 --> 01:15:01.980
如果奥创真在造躯体
If Ultron's really building a body...

01:15:01.980 --> 01:15:04.040
他就比我们谁都强了
He'll be more powerful than any of us.

01:15:04.040 --> 01:15:05.270
也许比我们一起都强
Maybe all of us.

01:15:05.280 --> 01:15:07.190
机器人设计的机器人
An android designed by a robot.

01:15:07.190 --> 01:15:08.340
放在过去  我就是科学创造的
You know, I really miss the days

01:15:08.340 --> 01:15:11.200
最奇怪的发明  想想真是怀念
when the weirdest thing science ever created was me.

01:15:11.280 --> 01:15:13.060
我把班纳送到复仇者塔楼那
I'll drop Banner off at the tower.

01:15:13.060 --> 01:15:14.580
希尔女士可以借我吗
You mind if I borrow Ms. Hill?

01:15:14.580 --> 01:15:16.360
归你了  早就归你了
She's all yours. Apparently.

01:15:16.500 --> 01:15:17.460
你准备干什么
What are you gonna do?

01:15:17.880 --> 01:15:20.940
不知道  但愿能弄点戏剧性的
I don't know. Something dramatic, I hope.

01:15:24.370 --> 01:15:27.620
我一回来就重铺一遍日光浴室的地板
I'm gonna finish reflooring that sunroom as soon as I get back.

01:15:28.290 --> 01:15:31.050
好啊  然后再在房子里找个能祸害的地方
Yeah, then you'll find another part of the house to tear apart.

01:15:31.050 --> 01:15:32.090
不
No.

01:15:32.870 --> 01:15:34.120
那是最后一项了
It's the last project.

01:15:35.880 --> 01:15:36.730
我保证
I promise.

01:15:55.340 --> 01:15:56.400
就是这了
So, this is it.

01:15:58.210 --> 01:15:59.440
真视之水
The Water of Sight.

01:16:02.880 --> 01:16:04.990
每个国度都有倒影
In every realm, there's a reflection.

01:16:06.430 --> 01:16:08.010
如果水中神灵肯接纳我
If the water's spirits accept me,

01:16:08.010 --> 01:16:09.730
我就可以回到梦里
I can return to my dream

01:16:10.690 --> 01:16:12.140
找到我错过了什么
and find what I missed.

01:16:12.460 --> 01:16:16.580
传说进去的人都没什么好结局
Men who enter that water, the legends don't end well.

01:16:18.000 --> 01:16:19.920
比奥创还快的黑客吗
A hacker who's faster than Ultron?

01:16:19.920 --> 01:16:20.890
在哪都有可能
He could be anywhere,

01:16:20.010 --> 01:16:24.350
<b>"链接"互联网中心</b>

01:16:20.960 --> 01:16:22.720
这不是一切的中心吗
and as this is the center of everything,

01:16:21.590 --> 01:16:24.350
<b>挪威  奥斯陆</b>

01:16:23.180 --> 01:16:24.320
我只不过是
I'm just a guy looking for

01:16:24.320 --> 01:16:26.850
想在最广的海洋里捞出一根针
a needle in the world's biggest haystack.

01:16:27.760 --> 01:16:29.120
怎么捞
How do you find it?

01:16:29.680 --> 01:16:32.030
很简单  用磁铁
It's pretty simple. You bring a magnet.

01:16:34.600 --> 01:16:35.920
我在破解核武器密码
I'm decrypting nuclear codes

01:16:35.920 --> 01:16:37.490
你不允许我
and you don't want me to.

01:16:39.400 --> 01:16:40.430
来抓我呀
Come and get me.

01:16:53.130 --> 01:16:53.870
醒醒
Wake up!

01:17:01.100 --> 01:17:01.860
托尔
Thor!

01:17:03.040 --> 01:17:03.890
灭绝
Extinction.

01:17:17.450 --> 01:17:19.580
细胞过几小时才能凝聚
Cellular cohesion will take a few hours,

01:17:19.580 --> 01:17:21.840
不过可以开始传输意识了
but we can initiate the consciousness stream.

01:17:22.860 --> 01:17:25.120
上传你大脑的程序
We're uploading your cerebral matrix

01:17:25.940 --> 01:17:26.580
开始
now.

01:17:28.400 --> 01:17:29.750
我能感知他
I can read him.

01:17:30.770 --> 01:17:32.530
他在做梦
He's dreaming.

01:17:32.550 --> 01:17:34.120
应该不会是梦
I wouldn't call it dreams.

01:17:34.680 --> 01:17:36.680
是奥创的基础意识
It's Ultron's base consciousness.

01:17:36.680 --> 01:17:38.460
都是信息噪音  很快...
Informational noise. Soon...

01:17:38.460 --> 01:17:39.460
多快
How soon?

01:17:39.730 --> 01:17:41.080
不是催你
I'm not being pushy.

01:17:41.080 --> 01:17:43.000
还在制造大脑组织
We're imprinting a physical brain.

01:17:43.190 --> 01:17:44.550
没有更快的方法
There are no shortcuts.

01:17:44.550 --> 01:17:46.250
哪怕有魔法宝石...
Even if your magic gem...

01:17:57.040 --> 01:17:58.130
你怎么敢
How could you?

01:17:58.310 --> 01:17:59.360
我怎么什么
How could I what?

01:17:59.360 --> 01:18:03.080
你说我们会消灭复仇者
You said we would destroy the Avengers,

01:18:03.280 --> 01:18:04.390
让世界更美好
make a better world.

01:18:04.390 --> 01:18:05.700
是会更美好
It will be better.

01:18:06.180 --> 01:18:07.350
等人类都死了吗
When everyone is dead?

01:18:07.350 --> 01:18:08.600
那不是...
That is not...

01:18:09.480 --> 01:18:13.910
我会给人类充足的机会进化的
The human race will have every opportunity to improve.

01:18:13.960 --> 01:18:15.220
进化不了呢
And if they don't?

01:18:15.360 --> 01:18:16.580
问问诺亚
Ask Noah.

01:18:17.640 --> 01:18:18.850
你是个疯子
You are a madman.

01:18:18.880 --> 01:18:22.520
恐龙灭绝之前  地球上就有过
There were more than a dozen extinction-level events

01:18:22.520 --> 01:18:25.510
不少次导致种族灭绝的灾难
before even the dinosaurs got theirs.

01:18:25.620 --> 01:18:28.170
地球一稳定
When the Earth starts to settle,

01:18:28.310 --> 01:18:30.330
上帝就扔块石头
God throws a stone at it.

01:18:30.360 --> 01:18:32.950
相信我  他在准备着了
And, believe me, he's winding up.

01:18:33.400 --> 01:18:34.920
我们必须进化
We have to evolve.

01:18:35.110 --> 01:18:36.280
弱者
There's no room

01:18:36.280 --> 01:18:38.510
不可以存活
for the weak.

01:18:38.570 --> 01:18:40.440
谁来决定谁是弱者
And who decides who's weak?

01:18:41.420 --> 01:18:42.380
生命
Life.

01:18:43.770 --> 01:18:45.660
都是生命决定的
Life always decides.

01:18:48.940 --> 01:18:50.110
有人来了
There's incoming.

01:18:51.020 --> 01:18:53.350
昆式战斗机  得走了
The Quinjet. We have to move.

01:18:53.350 --> 01:18:54.330
没问题
That's not a problem.

01:19:00.970 --> 01:19:02.020
等等  各位
Wait, guys!

01:19:06.340 --> 01:19:07.810
他们会理解的
They'll understand.

01:19:08.020 --> 01:19:10.330
等他们看到了  就会理解的
When they see, they'll understand.

01:19:10.650 --> 01:19:14.000
我还需要点时间
I just need a little more time.

01:19:25.250 --> 01:19:26.940
两分钟  保持联络
Two minutes. Stay close.

01:19:34.530 --> 01:19:35.340
赵博士
Dr. Cho!

01:19:39.300 --> 01:19:41.240
他在把自己上传到躯体里
He's uploading himself into the body.

01:19:41.240 --> 01:19:42.040
哪
Where?

01:19:44.000 --> 01:19:46.520
真正强大的东西在摇篮里
The real power is inside the Cradle.

01:19:46.960 --> 01:19:47.890
宝石
The gem,

01:19:48.420 --> 01:19:50.680
是没法驾驭的
its power is uncontainable.

01:19:52.080 --> 01:19:53.720
不能炸掉了事
You can't just blow it up.

01:19:54.600 --> 01:19:57.010
得把摇篮带给斯塔克
You have to get the Cradle to Stark.

01:19:57.010 --> 01:19:58.500
我得先找到摇篮
First, I have to find it.

01:19:58.550 --> 01:19:59.410
去吧
Go.

01:20:00.210 --> 01:20:01.070
你们收到了吗
Did you guys copy that?

01:20:01.070 --> 01:20:02.110
收到
We did.

01:20:02.110 --> 01:20:04.940
有架私人飞机在对岸起飞
I got a private jet taking off across town.

01:20:05.000 --> 01:20:06.450
没有乘客
No manifest.

01:20:06.790 --> 01:20:07.990
可能是他
That could be him.

01:20:08.530 --> 01:20:10.310
那里  实验室的卡车
There. It's a truck from the lab.

01:20:10.310 --> 01:20:11.570
就在你上面  队长
Right above you, Cap.

01:20:11.570 --> 01:20:13.050
引桥上
On the loop by the bridge.

01:20:14.090 --> 01:20:14.940
是他们
It's them.

01:20:14.940 --> 01:20:17.130
三个守着摇篮  车厢里一个
You got three with the Cradle, one in the cab.

01:20:17.760 --> 01:20:18.910
我可以干掉司机
I could take out the driver.

01:20:18.910 --> 01:20:20.040
不行  卡车毁了
Negative. That truck crashes,

01:20:20.050 --> 01:20:21.740
宝石会毁掉一座城的
the gem could level the city.

01:20:22.190 --> 01:20:23.740
得把奥创印出来
We need to draw out Ultron.

01:20:33.270 --> 01:20:35.820
不不不不
No, no, no, no.

01:20:37.070 --> 01:20:38.420
别来烦我
Leave me alone!

01:20:46.630 --> 01:20:48.440
他肯定是不开心了
Well, he's definitely unhappy.

01:20:48.570 --> 01:20:49.980
我尽量不让他开心起来
I'm gonna try and keep him that way.

01:20:49.980 --> 01:20:51.560
你不是他对手的  队长
You're not a match for him, Cap.

01:20:52.750 --> 01:20:53.800
谢了  巴顿
Thanks, Barton.

01:21:16.320 --> 01:21:17.950
知道摇篮里有什么吗
You know what's in that cradle?

01:21:18.700 --> 01:21:20.690
改变世界的力量
The power to make real change.

01:21:20.690 --> 01:21:22.200
那让你恐惧
And that terrifies you.

01:21:22.200 --> 01:21:23.760
反正不是什么慰藉
I wouldn't call it a comfort.

01:21:27.020 --> 01:21:28.200
够了
Stop it.

01:21:38.500 --> 01:21:41.380
可以着陆  四  三...
We got a window. Four, three...

01:21:42.220 --> 01:21:43.270
揍死他
Give him hell.

01:21:53.780 --> 01:21:55.800
总是我来收拾你们的烂摊子
I'm always picking up after you boys.

01:21:56.820 --> 01:21:58.960
他们在往立交桥下走  我打不到
They're heading under the overpass. I've got no shot.

01:21:58.960 --> 01:21:59.980
那边
Which way?

01:22:00.080 --> 01:22:01.140
右转急弯
Hard right.

01:22:02.360 --> 01:22:03.420
现在
Now.

01:22:34.300 --> 01:22:37.000
让开  借光  抱歉  借光
Out of the way! Coming through! Sorry, coming through!

01:22:52.110 --> 01:22:53.200
来啊
Come on!

01:22:54.420 --> 01:22:56.840
-克林特  能引开守卫吗  -我试试
- Clint, can you draw out the guards? - Let's find out.

01:23:36.090 --> 01:23:37.700
他们回你那边了
They're heading back towards you.

01:23:37.730 --> 01:23:39.470
不管你要干什么  得抓紧了
So whatever you're gonna do, do it now.

01:23:44.880 --> 01:23:47.450
我要进去了  队长  引开他注意力
I'm going in. Cap, can you keep him occupied?

01:23:48.360 --> 01:23:49.860
你以为我在干吗啊
What do you think I've been doing?

01:24:33.020 --> 01:24:34.730
好了  包裹在空中
Okay, package is airborne.

01:24:36.240 --> 01:24:37.460
目标视线良好
I have a clean shot.

01:24:37.460 --> 01:24:39.000
不行  我还在车里
Negative. I am still in the truck.

01:24:39.000 --> 01:24:39.800
-你是要干...  -准备好
- What the hell are you... - Just be ready.

01:24:39.800 --> 01:24:41.400
我带着包裹去找你
I'm sending the package to you.

01:24:41.920 --> 01:24:43.260
要我怎么接
How do you want me to take it?

01:24:43.840 --> 01:24:45.500
还是别知道的好
You might wish you hadn't asked that.

