Ultron thinks we're monsters.

01:38:25.780 --> 01:38:27.560
觉得我们才是世界的问题所在
That we're what's wrong with the world.

01:38:28.330 --> 01:38:30.070
这不仅仅是要打败他
This isn't just about beating him.

01:38:31.110 --> 01:38:32.600
还要看他说没说错
It's about whether he's right.

01:38:39.790 --> 01:38:40.910
娜塔莎
Natasha!

01:38:41.670 --> 01:38:42.700
娜塔莎
Natasha!

01:38:42.950 --> 01:38:43.960
布鲁斯
Bruce?

01:38:45.870 --> 01:38:47.010
没事吧
You all right?

01:38:47.120 --> 01:38:47.840
没事
Yeah.

01:38:47.840 --> 01:38:49.720
大伙都在城里  要开战了
The team is in the city. It's about to light up.

01:38:49.720 --> 01:38:52.070
你没找到钥匙什么的吧
I don't suppose you found a key lying around somewhere.

01:38:52.070 --> 01:38:54.460
找到了
Yeah. I did.

01:39:00.910 --> 01:39:02.110
我们怎么办
So what's our play?

01:39:02.120 --> 01:39:03.580
我是来护送你安全离开的
I'm here to get you to safety.

01:39:04.220 --> 01:39:05.350
任务还没完成
Job's not finished.

01:39:05.350 --> 01:39:06.680
我们可以帮忙疏散
We could help with the evacuation,

01:39:06.680 --> 01:39:09.280
但有平民  我就不能参战
but I can't be in a fight near civilians.

01:39:09.850 --> 01:39:11.260
你已经付出了不少
And you've done plenty.

01:39:13.680 --> 01:39:15.020
我们的战争结束了
Our fight is over.

01:39:16.580 --> 01:39:18.190
那就直接消失吗
So, we just disappear?

01:39:23.590 --> 01:39:24.640
快走
Come on.

01:39:29.260 --> 01:39:31.040
他在教堂  老大
Your man's in the church, boss.

01:39:31.870 --> 01:39:33.400
他应该在等你
I think he's waiting for you.

01:39:37.850 --> 01:39:39.990
来忏悔罪过吗
Come to confess your sins?

01:39:40.010 --> 01:39:41.210
不知道  你有多少时间
I don't know. How much time you got?

01:39:41.210 --> 01:39:42.440
反正比你多
More than you.

01:39:45.370 --> 01:39:48.040
你打药了吗  打了一针振金什么的
Have you been juicing? Little vibranium cocktail?

01:39:48.230 --> 01:39:50.420
你怎么...  我不想说"肿了"
You're looking... I don't wanna say "puffy."

01:39:50.420 --> 01:39:52.560
你在拖延时间  保护平民
You're stalling to protect the people.

01:39:52.760 --> 01:39:55.590
这就是任务  你忘了吗
Well, that is the mission. Did you forget?

01:39:55.700 --> 01:39:58.960
我早超越了你的任务  我是自由的
I've moved beyond your mission. I'm free.

01:40:03.100 --> 01:40:03.850
怎么
What?

01:40:05.120 --> 01:40:07.400
你以为只有你在拖延吗
You think you were the only one stalling?

01:40:08.090 --> 01:40:09.850
剩下的振金都在那
There's the rest of the vibranium.

01:40:09.850 --> 01:40:11.390
功能不明
Function, still unclear.

01:40:11.400 --> 01:40:13.610
这就是你的末日  托尼
This is how you end, Tony.

01:40:13.820 --> 01:40:15.760
我这个时代的和平
This is peace in my time.

01:40:32.350 --> 01:40:33.200
走
Go!

01:40:38.670 --> 01:40:40.070
快下桥
Get off the bridge!

01:40:44.470 --> 01:40:45.290
快跑
Run!

01:40:47.730 --> 01:40:48.740
奥创
Ultron.

01:40:54.780 --> 01:40:56.090
我的幻视
My Vision.

01:40:56.280 --> 01:40:58.680
他们真从我这夺走了一切
They really did take everything from me.

01:40:58.820 --> 01:41:00.880
你自己定的条款  可以自己改
You set the terms. You can change them.

01:41:00.890 --> 01:41:01.810
好吧
All right.

01:41:26.240 --> 01:41:27.420
周五  幻视呢
Friday, the Vision?

01:41:27.420 --> 01:41:28.380
成功了
Boss, it's working.

01:41:28.390 --> 01:41:29.660
他在把奥创和互联网隔离开
He's burning Ultron out of the net.

01:41:29.660 --> 01:41:31.280
这样他就逃不掉了
He won't escape through there.

01:41:36.130 --> 01:41:37.610
你把我封闭起来
You shut me out.

01:41:37.970 --> 01:41:39.410
你觉得我在乎吗
You think I care?

01:41:41.240 --> 01:41:42.930
你夺走我的世界
You take away my world,

01:41:43.380 --> 01:41:45.010
我就夺走你的
I take away yours.

01:42:29.840 --> 01:42:30.730
周五
Friday.

01:42:30.730 --> 01:42:33.250
索科威亚要飞起来了
Sokovia is going for a ride.

01:42:45.390 --> 01:42:46.830
能不能体会
Do you see

01:42:47.640 --> 01:42:49.290
这有多美
the beauty of it?

01:42:49.800 --> 01:42:51.390
这种必然
The inevitability.

01:42:51.970 --> 01:42:55.500
拼命登高  却只能坠落
You rise, only to fall.

01:42:57.980 --> 01:43:01.750
你们  复仇者  就是我的陨石
You, Avengers, you are my meteor.

01:43:01.750 --> 01:43:03.530
我除恶的利剑
My swift and terrible sword.

01:43:03.530 --> 01:43:05.530
你们的失败
And the earth will crack

01:43:05.530 --> 01:43:07.680
会毁灭整个地球
with the weight of your failure.

01:43:08.720 --> 01:43:13.020
把我从电脑里清除  让幻视跟我反目
Purge me from your computers, turn my own flesh against me.

01:43:13.270 --> 01:43:14.710
都没有意义
It means nothing.

01:43:14.710 --> 01:43:16.320
登到尘埃落定
When the dust settles,

01:43:16.470 --> 01:43:18.840
世上仅存的生物
the only thing living in this world

01:43:19.450 --> 01:43:20.820
就只剩下金属
will be metal.

01:43:25.600 --> 01:43:26.860
得走了
We gotta move.

01:43:27.220 --> 01:43:28.390
你不变绿吗
You're not gonna turn green?

01:43:28.390 --> 01:43:30.910
这种情况我必须保持清醒
I've got a compelling reason not to lose my cool.

01:43:31.460 --> 01:43:32.900
我喜欢你
I adore you.

01:43:41.320 --> 01:43:42.890
但我需要另一个家伙
But I need the other guy.

01:43:48.230 --> 01:43:49.820
来完成任务吧
Let's finish the job.

01:44:06.640 --> 01:44:08.560
这下算扯平了吧
I really hope this makes us even.

01:44:10.430 --> 01:44:11.760
去做英雄吧
Now go be a hero.

01:44:20.980 --> 01:44:23.190
振金做的核心有磁场
The vibranium core's got a magnetic field.

01:44:23.190 --> 01:44:24.940
能让城下的土地聚在一起
That's what's keeping the rock together.

01:44:24.940 --> 01:44:25.450
如果落下呢
If it drops?

01:44:25.460 --> 01:44:27.430
现在的话  死伤成千上万
Right now, the impact will kill thousands.

01:44:27.430 --> 01:44:30.540
高度足够的话  会毁灭全世界
Once it gets high enough? Global extinction.

01:44:34.560 --> 01:44:36.850
楼里还有人  十楼
That building's not clear. The 10th floor.

01:44:43.760 --> 01:44:45.070
好了
Okay.

01:44:45.170 --> 01:44:46.330
进浴缸
Get in the tub!

01:44:52.980 --> 01:44:55.300
有空中单位  向桥的方向去了
I got airborne, heading up to the bridge.

01:44:57.680 --> 01:44:58.970
队长  有东西过去了
Cap, you got incoming.

01:44:58.970 --> 01:45:00.460
来了都走了
Incoming already came in.

01:45:03.520 --> 01:45:06.050
斯塔克  你想办法让城市安全降落
Stark, you worry about bringing the city back down safely.

01:45:06.430 --> 01:45:07.970
剩下的人就一个目标
The rest of us have one job,

01:45:08.180 --> 01:45:09.790
把他们都毁了
tear these things apart.

01:45:10.030 --> 01:45:12.140
受伤了  就打伤他们
You get hurt, hurt them back.

01:45:12.310 --> 01:45:13.350
没了命
You get killed,

01:45:14.310 --> 01:45:15.430
撑住接着打
walk it off.

01:45:50.290 --> 01:45:51.460
走走走
Go, go, go!

01:45:56.420 --> 01:45:57.970
我怎么会造成了这一切
How could I let this happen?

01:45:57.970 --> 01:45:59.510
你没事吧
Hey, hey, you okay?

01:45:59.950 --> 01:46:00.840
都是我们的错
This is all our fault.

01:46:00.840 --> 01:46:01.850
看着我
Hey, look at me.

01:46:02.120 --> 01:46:04.670
是你的错  是大家的错  谁在乎呢
It's your fault, it's everyone's fault. Who cares?

01:46:04.680 --> 01:46:06.040
你能应付这个吗
Are you up for this?

01:46:06.170 --> 01:46:07.180
能吗
Are you?

01:46:07.850 --> 01:46:10.750
我得弄明白  因为城市已经飞起来了
Look, I just need to know. Because the city is flying.

01:46:11.120 --> 01:46:14.780
听我说  城市飞起来了  我们在对战机器大军
Okay. Look, the city is flying, we're fighting an army of robots,

01:46:15.870 --> 01:46:17.320
而我只有弓箭
and I have a bow and arrow.

01:46:17.320 --> 01:46:18.880
这一切简直太扯了
None of this makes sense.

01:46:21.730 --> 01:46:24.290
但我准备回到战场  因为这是我的职责
But I'm going back out there because it's my job.

01:46:24.560 --> 01:46:27.250
但我没法边干工作边哄你
Okay? And I can't do my job and babysit.

01:46:27.500 --> 01:46:30.570
你做过什么  你之前是谁都不重要
It doesn't matter what you did or what you were.

01:46:30.860 --> 01:46:33.910
出去了就要战斗  毁掉他们
If you go out there, you fight, and you fight to kill.

01:46:34.220 --> 01:46:35.690
待在这也没事
Stay in here, you're good.

01:46:35.690 --> 01:46:36.950
我会叫你哥哥来找你
I'll send your brother to come find you.

01:46:36.960 --> 01:46:38.900
但只要你踏出去
But if you step out that door,

01:46:39.660 --> 01:46:41.060
你就是复仇者的一员
you are an Avenger.

01:46:45.790 --> 01:46:47.270
好了  聊得很开心
All right. Good chat.

01:46:51.170 --> 01:46:52.950
是啊  城市都飞起来了
Yeah, the city is flying.

01:47:26.200 --> 01:47:27.270
抓住你了
I got you!

01:47:27.820 --> 01:47:29.020
看着我
Just look at me!

01:47:35.380 --> 01:47:37.540
你没法救所有人
You can't save them all.

01:47:38.920 --> 01:47:40.040
你永远不可能...
You'll never...

01:47:40.670 --> 01:47:41.750
不可能什么
"Never" what?

01:47:41.840 --> 01:47:43.420
话都不说完
You didn't finish!

01:47:46.810 --> 01:47:48.150
你刚在打盹吗
What, were you napping?

01:48:10.400 --> 01:48:11.430
托尔
Thor.

01:48:13.260 --> 01:48:15.270
你真是让我烦
You're bothering me.

01:48:50.800 --> 01:48:51.680
好了  这片安全
All right, we're all clear here.

01:48:51.680 --> 01:48:53.230
这片还不安全
We are not clear!

01:48:53.250 --> 01:48:54.840
差得远呢
We are very not clear!

01:48:57.530 --> 01:48:58.850
好了  朝你那去了
All right, coming to you.

01:48:59.400 --> 01:49:00.610
快点走  老爷爷
Keep up, old man!

01:49:03.340 --> 01:49:04.740
没人会知道的
Nobody would know.

01:49:05.570 --> 01:49:06.590
没人
Nobody.

01:49:08.580 --> 01:49:10.730
"最后见到他时  奥创坐在他身上
"The last I saw him, an Ultron was sitting on him.

01:49:10.730 --> 01:49:13.670
"是啊  会怀念他的  飞快的小混蛋
"Yeah, he'll be missed, that quick little bastard.

01:49:13.670 --> 01:49:15.000
"我已经想他了"
"I miss him already."

01:49:30.170 --> 01:49:32.550
先停火
Hold your fire!

01:49:41.150 --> 01:49:42.220
罗曼诺夫
Romanoff!

01:49:42.810 --> 01:49:43.780
谢了
Thanks!

01:49:53.190 --> 01:49:54.830
反重力装置设定好了  会反转
The anti-gravs are rigged to flip.

01:49:54.830 --> 01:49:57.080
碰一下就会全力向下
Touch them, they'll go full reverse thrust.

01:49:57.080 --> 01:49:58.630
而且是飞速向下
The city's not coming down slow.

01:49:58.630 --> 01:50:00.140
振金是核心
Spire is vibranium.

01:50:00.240 --> 01:50:01.210
如果托尔能打一下...
If I get Thor to hit it...

01:50:01.210 --> 01:50:02.970
装置会失效  但还不够
It will crack. That's not enough.

01:50:02.970 --> 01:50:04.430
后果仍然很严重
The impact would still be devastating.

01:50:04.430 --> 01:50:06.010
如果封住一端呢
Maybe if we can cap the other end.

01:50:06.010 --> 01:50:07.890
把能量都逼回装置里
Keep the atomic action doubling back.

01:50:07.890 --> 01:50:09.600
那会让整座城蒸发的
That could vaporize the city.

01:50:10.090 --> 01:50:11.410
还有城里的人
And everyone on it.

01:50:18.170 --> 01:50:19.690
下一波马上就来
The next wave is gonna hit any minute.

01:50:19.690 --> 01:50:22.040
-有进展没  斯塔克  -没什么好主意
- What do you got, Stark? - Nothing great.

01:50:22.610 --> 01:50:24.390
也许有个办法炸毁城市
Maybe a way to blow up the city.

01:50:24.910 --> 01:50:26.370
不让城市撞击地球
That'll keep it from impacting the surface,

01:50:26.370 --> 01:50:27.730
当然你们得先撤
if you guys can get clear.

01:50:27.730 --> 01:50:29.930
我要解决方案  不是逃跑方案
I asked for a solution, not an escape plan.

01:50:29.940 --> 01:50:32.460
冲击半径在不断增加
Impact radius is getting bigger every second.

01:50:32.940 --> 01:50:34.440
得赶紧做出选择
We're gonna have to make a choice.

01:50:35.160 --> 01:50:36.990
队长  这些人无处可去
Cap, these people are going nowhere.

01:50:37.450 --> 01:50:38.940
如果斯塔克有法子毁了这...
If Stark finds a way to blow this rock...

01:50:38.940 --> 01:50:40.360
先带所有人撤离
Not till everyone's safe.

01:50:40.540 --> 01:50:42.050
是毁灭这里的人
Everyone up here versus

01:50:42.050 --> 01:50:43.780
还是毁灭所有地球人  这不用算的
everyone down there? There's no math there.

01:50:43.790 --> 01:50:45.690
这里还有平民  我就不离开
I'm not leaving this rock with one civilian on it.

01:50:45.690 --> 01:50:47.170
我没说要走
I didn't say we should leave.

01:50:50.040 --> 01:50:51.460
还有更惨的死法的
There's worse ways to go.

01:50:56.800 --> 01:50:58.830
上哪看这样的美景呢
Where else am I gonna get a view like this?

01:51:01.050 --> 01:51:03.240
你喜欢美景真好  罗曼诺夫
Glad you like the view, Romanoff.

01:51:03.580 --> 01:51:05.000
美的还在后头呢
It's about to get better.

01:51:29.160 --> 01:51:30.360
漂亮吧
Nice, right?

01:51:30.470 --> 01:51:32.960
从箱底翻出来的  还有几个老朋友
Pulled her out of mothballs with a couple of old friends.

01:51:32.960 --> 01:51:35.040
虽然有点灰  但还能用
She's dusty, but she'll do.

01:51:35.040 --> 01:51:36.950
弗瑞  你个老混蛋
Fury, you son of a bitch.

01:51:37.300 --> 01:51:38.740
嘴这么脏  怎么吻你妈
You kiss your mother with that mouth?

01:51:38.750 --> 01:51:41.510
高度18000英尺  还在升高
Altitude is 18,000 and climbing.

01:51:41.510 --> 01:51:42.850
准备部署救生舱
Lifeboats secure to deploy.

01:51:42.850 --> 01:51:46.100
倒计时三  二
Disengage in three, two...

01:51:47.290 --> 01:51:48.440
出发
Take them out.

01:51:57.570 --> 01:51:58.790
这是神盾局吗
This is S.H.I.E.L.D.?

01:51:59.430 --> 01:52:01.420
这是神盾局该有的样子
This is what S.H.I.E.L.D. Is supposed to be.

01:52:03.580 --> 01:52:04.960
还不赖嘛
This is not so bad.

01:52:08.280 --> 01:52:09.400
带大家上
Let's load them up.

01:52:15.090 --> 01:52:18.750
长官  右舷纠集了数架敌机
Sir, we have multiple bogies converging on our starboard flank.

01:52:19.000 --> 01:52:20.560
给他们点颜色
Show 'em what we got.

01:52:20.930 --> 01:52:21.850
上吧
You're up.

01:52:26.910 --> 01:52:27.910
棒
Yes!

01:52:28.090 --> 01:52:30.320
这回可有的讲了
Now this is gonna be a good story.

01:52:32.560 --> 01:52:35.020
是啊  但你得先活下来
Yup. If you live to tell it.

01:52:35.040 --> 01:52:36.570
你觉得我自己办不到[握我自己的]吗
You think I can't hold my own?

01:52:36.850 --> 01:52:38.400
这次成功了  我来握住你的
We get through this, I'll hold your own.

01:52:38.400 --> 01:52:40.200
到你嘴里就变了味
You had to make it weird.

01:52:45.140 --> 01:52:47.930
这群人之后还有50到100个
I got about 50 to 100 more coming in after this group.

01:53:05.300 --> 01:53:07.070
快走  快走  走吧
Here we go. Here we go. Let's move.

01:53:07.070 --> 01:53:08.350
快走
Let's go, everyone!

01:53:10.530 --> 01:53:12.510
六号舱已全部  锁定...
Number six boat is topped and locked...

01:53:12.510 --> 01:53:14.880
Lock, stock and barrel

01:53:12.510 --> 01:53:14.880
全员...  到头...
Or stocked... Topped...

01:53:14.880 --> 01:53:17.320
人已经满了
It's full of people.

01:53:18.870 --> 01:53:20.330
敌机来袭
Incoming!

01:53:22.860 --> 01:53:24.210
我的天
Oh, God!

01:53:34.440 --> 01:53:36.380
你觉得你能救谁吗
You think you're saving anyone?

01:53:37.510 --> 01:53:40.050
我转一下  早一点让这座城掉下去
I turn that key and drop this rock a little early

01:53:40.050 --> 01:53:42.300
还是会死伤上亿
and it's still billions dead.

01:53:42.300 --> 01:53:43.660
连你也不能阻止
Even you can't stop that.

01:53:43.660 --> 01:53:46.210
我是托尔  奥丁之子
I am Thor, son of Odin,

01:53:46.210 --> 01:53:48.550
只要我还有一口气...
and as long as there is life in my breast...

01:53:48.550 --> 01:53:51.410
我想不出词了
I am running out of things to say!

01:53:51.420 --> 01:53:52.440
准备好了吗
Are you ready?

01:53:59.740 --> 01:54:01.240
这锤子重量分布得真好
It's terribly well-balanced.

01:54:01.250 --> 01:54:02.490
要是锤头太重
Well, if there's too much weight,

01:54:02.490 --> 01:54:04.460
挥起来会损失力量  所以...
you lose power on the swing, so...

01:54:05.640 --> 01:54:08.710
有了  弄个热能护罩
I got it. Create a heat seal.

01:54:09.000 --> 01:54:09.910
我可以...
I could...

01:54:09.910 --> 01:54:12.040
我可以在底下让装置过载
I could supercharge the spire from below.

01:54:12.040 --> 01:54:13.530
计算中
Running numbers.

01:54:23.700 --> 01:54:25.770
能量够的话  热护罩可以成功
A heat seal could work with enough power.

01:54:25.780 --> 01:54:28.070
-托尔  我有计划了  -没时间了
- Thor, I got a plan. - We're out of time.

01:54:28.070 --> 01:54:29.230
他们冲着核心来了
They're coming for the core.

01:54:29.230 --> 01:54:31.310
罗德  送其他人上救生舱
Rhodey, get the rest of the people on board that carrier.

01:54:31.310 --> 01:54:31.810
好的
On it.

01:54:31.810 --> 01:54:34.280
复仇者  该搏回命了
Avengers, time to work for a living.

01:54:43.610 --> 01:54:45.310
-没事吧  -没事
- Are you good? - Yeah.

01:54:46.280 --> 01:54:47.470
罗曼诺夫
Romanoff.

01:54:47.470 --> 01:54:50.180
你和班纳不是打算鸳鸯双飞  一起隐居吧
You and Banner better not be playing "hide the zucchini."

01:54:50.180 --> 01:54:51.540
别激动  铁头
Relax, shellhead.

01:54:51.540 --> 01:54:53.300
还有人不会飞呢
Not all of us can fly.

01:54:58.580 --> 01:55:00.600
-你什么打算[钻头]  -这就是
- What's the drill? - This is the drill.

01:55:00.600 --> 01:55:03.380
让奥创碰到核心  我们就失败了
If Ultron gets a hand on the core, we lose.

01:55:07.140 --> 01:55:08.990
你们就这点能耐吗
Is that the best you can do?

01:55:19.110 --> 01:55:20.540
非得好心问一下
You had to ask.

01:55:20.560 --> 01:55:23.040
这就是我的能耐
This is the best I can do.

01:55:23.230 --> 01:55:25.210
我就想这样
This is exactly what I wanted.

01:55:25.210 --> 01:55:26.390
你们所有人
All of you

01:55:26.390 --> 01:55:28.400
对阵所有的我
against all of me.

01:55:28.590 --> 01:55:31.260
你们怎么可能阻止我
How can you possibly hope to stop me?

01:55:31.700 --> 01:55:34.210
老爷子说过...
Well, like the old man said...

01:55:35.200 --> 01:55:36.200
齐心协力
together.

01:57:05.030 --> 01:57:07.820
我事后诸葛亮一下...
You know, with the benefit of hindsight...

01:57:16.430 --> 01:57:17.480
他们想逃离城市
They'll try to leave the city.

01:57:17.480 --> 01:57:19.810
不可以  一个也不能放  罗德
We can't let them, not even one. Rhodey.

01:57:19.810 --> 01:57:20.800
收到
I'm on it.

01:57:21.330 --> 01:57:23.000
没让你走呢
No. I didn't say you could leave.

01:57:23.000 --> 01:57:25.420
战争机器来了  就在...
War Machine coming at you! Right...

01:57:31.710 --> 01:57:33.120
这是什么
Okay, what?

01:57:33.120 --> 01:57:35.240
得撤了  我都能感觉到空气变稀薄了
We gotta move out. Even I can tell the air is getting thin.

01:57:35.240 --> 01:57:36.720
你们去救生舱
You guys get to the boats.

01:57:36.720 --> 01:57:38.850
我再找一下有没有漏的  一会找你们
I'll sweep for stragglers. Be right behind you.

01:57:38.850 --> 01:57:40.060
核心呢
What about the core?

01:57:40.610 --> 01:57:41.940
我来保护
I'll protect it.

01:57:43.370 --> 01:57:44.460
这是我的职责
It's my job.

01:57:46.020 --> 01:57:46.910
小娜
Nat.

01:57:46.990 --> 01:57:47.890
这边
This way.

01:57:52.270 --> 01:57:53.520
带人们上救生舱
Get the people on the boats.

01:57:53.520 --> 01:57:54.470
我不能把你留在这
I'm not going to leave you here.

01:57:54.480 --> 01:57:55.970
我能应付这个
I can handle this.

01:57:57.920 --> 01:57:59.300
等大家都撤了再回来
Come back for me when everyone else is off.

01:57:59.300 --> 01:58:00.320
一个也不能少
Not before.

01:58:01.230 --> 01:58:02.380
明白吗
You understand?

01:58:03.680 --> 01:58:05.940
我可是比你大了12分钟
You know, I'm 12 minutes older than you.

01:58:05.940 --> 01:58:06.930
去吧
Go.

01:58:08.520 --> 01:58:10.080
老大  能量已经远低于...
Boss, power levels are way below...

01:58:10.080 --> 01:58:12.750
重新分配能源  只有一次机会
Reroute everything. We get one shot at this.

01:58:16.740 --> 01:58:18.240
我知道需要干什么
I know what I need to do.

01:58:18.910 --> 01:58:20.100
餐厅
The dining room.

01:58:20.170 --> 01:58:22.080
把东面的墙拆掉
If I knock out that east wall,

01:58:22.080 --> 01:58:24.400
劳拉就有了工作的地方
it'd make a nice workspace for Laura, huh?

01:58:25.140 --> 01:58:26.660
周围挡一下
Put up some baffling.

01:58:26.660 --> 01:58:28.480
她听不到孩子们乱跑的  怎么样
She can't hear the kids running around. What do you think?

01:58:28.480 --> 01:58:30.210
反正你们总在厨房吃
You guys always eat in the kitchen anyway.

01:58:30.210 --> 01:58:31.960
谁在餐厅吃饭啊
No one eats in a dining room.

01:58:37.340 --> 01:58:38.710
时间不多了
We don't have a lot of time.

01:58:39.100 --> 01:58:40.550
赶紧上救生舱
So get your ass on a boat.

01:58:53.880 --> 01:58:55.010
大家伙
Hey, big guy.

01:58:56.770 --> 01:58:58.420
太阳就要下山了
Sun's getting real low.

01:58:59.130 --> 01:59:01.820
你安全了  没事的  系好安全带
You're safe now. You're gonna be okay. Buckle up.

01:59:04.540 --> 01:59:05.920
保管好自己的物品  抓紧就坐
Secure your gear, find a seat.

01:59:05.920 --> 01:59:06.810
科斯特尔
Costel!

01:59:08.180 --> 01:59:09.710
我们之前一起在市场
We were in the market.

01:59:10.330 --> 01:59:11.410
科斯特尔
Costel!

01:59:25.440 --> 01:59:27.350
托尔  我需要你回教堂
Thor, I'm gonna need you back in the church.

01:59:27.350 --> 01:59:29.240
-就这些人了吗  -嗯
- Is this the last of them? - Yeah.

01:59:29.250 --> 01:59:30.580
其他人都上航母了
Everyone else is on the carrier.

01:59:30.580 --> 01:59:32.060
如果这次成功了
You know, this works,

01:59:32.370 --> 01:59:34.050
我们可能活不下来
we maybe don't walk away.

01:59:34.620 --> 01:59:35.550
没准吧
Maybe not.

01:59:54.710 --> 01:59:58.410
没有了束缚  我开心地玩
I got no strings, so I have fun

01:59:58.490 --> 02:00:01.750
不被任何人约束
I'm not tied up to anyone.

02:00:02.810 --> 02:00:04.030
快点  走吧
Come on. Time to go.

02:00:36.700 --> 02:00:38.290
你没预见到吗
You didn't see that coming?

02:01:34.810 --> 02:01:36.780
我的天呐
For God's sake.

02:01:53.130 --> 02:01:55.510
-泽林卡  -科斯特尔  宝贝
- Zrinka! - Costel! Baby!

02:02:07.130 --> 02:02:08.460
不  不  我没事
No, no, I'm fine.

02:02:08.640 --> 02:02:09.600
没事
Fine.

02:02:11.170 --> 02:02:13.170
今天真是漫长
It's been a long day.

02:02:27.890 --> 02:02:29.140
旺达
Wanda.

02:02:29.730 --> 02:02:33.370
你留在这会死的
If you stay here, you'll die.

02:02:34.520 --> 02:02:35.960
我刚死过
I just did.

02:02:36.770 --> 02:02:38.700
你知道什么感觉吗
Do you know how it felt?

02:02:52.600 --> 02:02:54.800
就这种感觉
It felt like that.

02:03:29.840 --> 02:03:31.770
托尔  等我口令
Thor, on my mark.

02:03:47.120 --> 02:03:48.110
动手
Now!

02:04:15.680 --> 02:04:18.620
大家伙  我们成功了
Hey, big guy. We did it.

02:04:19.120 --> 02:04:20.430
任务完成了
The job is finished.

02:04:21.010 --> 02:04:23.180
现在你得驾驶飞机返航
Now I need you to turn this bird around, okay?

02:04:28.220 --> 02:04:30.400
隐匿模式追踪不到你
We can't track you in stealth mode.

02:04:31.990 --> 02:04:34.540
帮我个忙  我需要你...
So help me out. I need you...

02:05:19.700 --> 02:05:20.970
你怕了
You're afraid.

02:05:21.770 --> 02:05:22.890
怕你吗
Of you?

02:05:23.420 --> 02:05:24.430
怕死亡
Of death.

02:05:25.350 --> 02:05:26.660
你是最后一个
You're the last one.

02:05:27.390 --> 02:05:29.590
你本该是最后一个
You were supposed to be the last.

02:05:30.110 --> 02:05:32.120
斯塔克想造救世主
Stark asked for a savior

02:05:32.940 --> 02:05:35.030
却甘心得到个奴隶
and settled for a slave.

02:05:35.270 --> 02:05:37.870
看来我们都让人失望了
I suppose we are both disappointments.

02:05:40.100 --> 02:05:41.370
是啊
I suppose we are.

02:05:41.980 --> 02:05:43.370
人类真奇怪
Humans are odd.

02:05:45.020 --> 02:05:48.160
他们觉得秩序与混乱是相对的
They think order and chaos are somehow opposites

02:05:48.160 --> 02:05:52.580
想控制自己无力掌控的
and try to control what won't be.

02:05:53.410 --> 02:05:55.600
但他们的努力值得尊敬
But there is grace in their failings.

02:05:56.410 --> 02:05:57.890
你没注意到吧
I think you missed that.

02:05:59.070 --> 02:06:00.430
他们注定灭亡
They're doomed.

02:06:01.020 --> 02:06:01.980
是啊
Yes.

02:06:06.140 --> 02:06:09.360
但事物的美  并不在能否长久
But a thing isn't beautiful because it lasts.

02:06:11.330 --> 02:06:13.240
身为他们的一员很荣幸
It's a privilege to be among them.

02:06:13.500 --> 02:06:16.170
你真是天真到无可救药
You're unbearably naive.

02:06:16.390 --> 02:06:17.380
这个嘛
Well...

02:06:19.480 --> 02:06:21.240
毕竟我昨天才出生
I was born yesterday.

02:07:11.600 --> 02:07:15.890
<b>新复仇者联盟总部</b>

02:07:13.020 --> 02:07:15.890
<b>纽约州北部</b>

02:07:34.080 --> 02:07:36.290
<b>内特尼尔·皮特·巴顿</b>

02:07:34.110 --> 02:07:36.240
看  来见见小娜阿姨
Look! Say hi to Auntie Nat!

02:07:37.600 --> 02:07:38.590
胖墩
Fat.

02:07:39.470 --> 02:07:41.720
有个技术员标记了这个
One of our tech boys flagged this.

02:07:42.010 --> 02:07:44.180
在班达海[印尼]坠毁了
Splashed down in the Banda Sea.

02:07:45.510 --> 02:07:47.100
可能是昆式战机
Could be the Quinjet.

02:07:47.320 --> 02:07:48.980
但是有斯塔克的隐匿技术
But with Stark's stealth tech,

02:07:48.980 --> 02:07:50.980
我们根本搜索不到
we still can't track the damn thing.

02:07:52.220 --> 02:07:53.330
好吧
Right.

02:07:54.050 --> 02:07:56.560
有可能跳机游到了斐济
Probably jumped out and swam to Fiji.

02:07:57.610 --> 02:07:59.070
他会寄明信片的
He'll send a postcard.

02:07:59.560 --> 02:08:00.750
"真希望你在这"
"Wish you were here."

02:08:03.450 --> 02:08:06.760
当初是你派我招募的他
You sent me to recruit him way back when.

02:08:08.470 --> 02:08:10.500
你那时知道会发生什么吗
Did you know then what was gonna happen?

02:08:13.330 --> 02:08:14.510
怎么可能知道
You never know.

02:08:15.460 --> 02:08:18.640
只能先尽人事  再听天命了
You hope for the best, then make do with what you get.

02:08:19.440 --> 02:08:20.730
我的团队不错
I got a great team.

02:08:21.990 --> 02:08:23.670
没什么是永久的
Nothing lasts forever.

02:08:24.360 --> 02:08:26.160
麻烦永远在  罗曼诺夫小姐
Trouble, Ms. Romanoff.

02:08:26.560 --> 02:08:30.230
不管谁赢谁输  麻烦总是免不了的
No matter who wins or loses, trouble still comes around.

02:08:33.740 --> 02:08:35.170
规则已经变了
The rules have changed.

02:08:35.170 --> 02:08:36.410
这是个新东西
We're dealing with something new.

02:08:36.410 --> 02:08:38.210
幻视是人工智能
The Vision is artificial intelligence.

02:08:38.210 --> 02:08:40.290
-一台机器  -所以不算吗
- A machine. - So, it doesn't count?

02:08:40.290 --> 02:08:42.570
举锤子的不是个人
No, it's not like a person lifting the hammer.

02:08:42.570 --> 02:08:43.820
是啊  到我们这就不一样了
Right, different rules for us.

02:08:43.820 --> 02:08:45.590
-他是个好人  人造的  -谢谢
- Nice guy. Artificial. - Thank you.

02:08:45.590 --> 02:08:48.400
他能举起锤子  就有资格留着意识宝石
He can wield the hammer, he can keep the Mind Stone.

02:08:49.520 --> 02:08:51.290
宝石在幻视那很安全
It's safe with the Vision.

02:08:51.810 --> 02:08:54.110
这年头安全可不好找
And these days, safe is in short supply.

02:08:56.450 --> 02:08:58.190
可是要是放在电梯里
But if you put the hammer in an elevator...

02:08:58.190 --> 02:09:00.110
-锤子会被举起来  -电梯配不上呢
- It would still go up. - Elevator's not worthy.

02:09:00.110 --> 02:09:02.140
我会怀念你俩的贫嘴的
I'm gonna miss these little talks of ours.

02:09:02.140 --> 02:09:03.320
不走就不会
Not if you don't leave.

02:09:04.080 --> 02:09:05.360
我没得选
I have no choice.

02:09:05.760 --> 02:09:08.070
意识宝石是过去几年
The Mind Stone is the fourth of the Infinity Stones

02:09:08.070 --> 02:09:09.760
出现的第四颗无限宝石
to show up in the last few years.

02:09:09.760 --> 02:09:11.180
绝不是巧合
It's not a coincidence.

02:09:12.170 --> 02:09:13.930
有人在下一盘大棋
Someone has been playing an intricate game

02:09:13.930 --> 02:09:15.670
把我们当棋子
and has made pawns of us.

02:09:15.880 --> 02:09:17.830
如果所有宝石都就位了
And once all these pieces are in position...

02:09:17.830 --> 02:09:19.080
三个大同花
Triple Yahtzee.

02:09:19.410 --> 02:09:21.020
你觉得你能查明怎么回事吗
You think you can find out what's coming?

02:09:21.020 --> 02:09:21.970
能
I do.

02:09:22.890 --> 02:09:24.210
除了这家伙
Besides this one,

02:09:24.570 --> 02:09:26.420
没有解释不了的东西
there's nothing that can't be explained.

02:09:34.210 --> 02:09:37.320
这人真不懂得爱护草坪
That man has no regard for lawn maintenance.

02:09:39.940 --> 02:09:42.490
我倒是会怀念他的  你也会想我的
I'm gonna miss him, though. And you're gonna miss me.

02:09:42.610 --> 02:09:44.780
男子汉这回要掉不少泪呢
There's gonna be a lot of manful tears.

02:09:46.330 --> 02:09:47.630
我会想你的  托尼
I will miss you, Tony.

02:09:48.090 --> 02:09:49.110
是吗
Yeah?

02:09:49.450 --> 02:09:51.700
我是该撤了
Well, it's time for me to tap out.

02:09:52.250 --> 02:09:54.480
我也许应该跟巴顿学点经验
Maybe I should take a page out of Barton's book.

02:09:54.480 --> 02:09:57.430
给小辣椒建个农场  希望没人去炸
Build Pepper a farm, hope nobody blows it up.

02:09:58.170 --> 02:09:59.340
简单的生活
The simple life.

02:09:59.630 --> 02:10:00.790
你会有那天的
You'll get there one day.

02:10:01.290 --> 02:10:02.260
我也不知道
I don't know.

02:10:02.310 --> 02:10:04.460
成家  稳定...
Family, stability...

02:10:05.640 --> 02:10:08.640
渴望那些的我75年前被冻进冰块里了
The guy who wanted all that went in the ice 75 years ago.

02:10:10.510 --> 02:10:12.040
出来的是另一个我了
I think someone else came out.

02:10:16.660 --> 02:10:17.640
你还好吧
You all right?

02:10:19.920 --> 02:10:20.910
我在家里
I'm home.

02:10:29.380 --> 02:10:31.920
你是想盯着墙看还是想去工作
You wanna keep staring at the wall, or do you wanna go to work?

02:10:32.280 --> 02:10:33.550
那堵墙是挺有意思的
I mean, it's a pretty interesting wall.

02:10:33.550 --> 02:10:36.450
你不是和托尼深情对视呢吗
I thought you and Tony were still gazing into each other's eyes.

02:10:37.020 --> 02:10:38.110
怎么样
How do we look?

02:10:38.240 --> 02:10:40.500
反正算不上传奇队伍
Well, we're not the '27 Yankees.

02:10:40.530 --> 02:10:41.740
还是有几个大牌的
We got some hitters.

02:10:42.380 --> 02:10:44.880
是不错  但还不是团队
They're good. They're not a team.

02:10:45.020 --> 02:10:46.570
来调教一下他们吧
Let's beat them into shape.

02:11:05.120 --> 02:11:06.370
复仇者...
Avengers...

02:13:25.540 --> 02:13:26.690
好吧
Fine.

02:13:28.270 --> 02:13:30.500
我自己来
I'll do it myself.
